wlers%20Ahead%20Of%20Asia%20Cup%20Clash%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20time%20for%20an%20India%20vs%20Pakistan%20battle%20in%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20has%20arrived%2C%20with%20the%20two%20Asian%20giants%20set%20to%20square-off%20in%20the%20group%20stage%20of%20the%20tournament.%20More%20often%20than%20not%2C%20the%20event%20is%20dubbed%20as%20a%20contest%20between%20Pakistan's%20bowling%20and%20India's%20batting.%20Just%20like%20the%20cricketing%20universe%2C%20even%20India's%20batting%20talisman%20Virat%20Kohli%20is%20in%20awe%20of%20Pakistan's%20bowling%20attack.%20He%20Kohli%20feels%20one%20has%20to%20be%20at%20his%20absolute%20best%20to%20face%20a%20high-quality%20bowling%20attack%20like%20Pakistan's.%20The%20Indians%20have%20won%20their%20last%20three%20ODIs%20against%20Pakistan%20but%20the%20last%20one%20was%20played%20during%20the%202019%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20feel%20bowling%20is%20their%20strength.%20And%20they've%20got%20some%20really%20impactful%20bowlers%20that%20can%20change%20the%20course%20of%20the%20game%20anytime%20based%20on%20their%20skill%20set.%20So%2C%20you%20have%20to%20be%20at%20your%20absolute%20best%20to%20face%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20Star%20Sports%20ahead%20of%20the%20start%20of%20India's%20Asia%20Cup%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKohli%20has%20been%20in%20decent%20form%20in%20ODIs%20lately%2C%20having%20scripted%20554%20runs%20in%2013%20matches%20in%20the%20format%20since%20last%20December%20at%20a%20commendable%20average%20of%2050.36.%20Talking%20about%20his%20approach%20lately%2C%20Kohli%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20only%20try%20to%20understand%20how%20I%20can%20better%20my%20game.%20Every%20day%2C%20every%20practice%20session%2C%20every%20year%2C%20every%20season%2C%20this%20is%20what%20has%20helped%20me%20play%20this%20well%20for%20so%20long%20and%20to%20perform%20for%20my%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20you%20can%20perform%20consistently%20without%20that%20mindset%20because%20if%20your%20performance%20is%20your%20only%20goal%2C%20then%20you%20can%20be%20satisfied%20and%20stop%20working%20hard.%20There%20is%20no%20limit%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20set%20achievement%20that%20if%20you%20reach%20a%20certain%20stage%2C%20you've%20reached%20excellence.%20I%20think%20I%20strive%20for%20betterment%20every%20day%2C%20so%20that%20is%20a%20better%20word%20to%20use%2C%20and%20yes%2C%20performance%20obviously%20becomes%20a%20by-product%20because%20your%20mindset%20is%20%E2%80%98How%20do%20I%20make%20my%20team%20win%20from%20this%20position%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693532040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2Figis7_kohli-six_625x300_04_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fwhat-virat-kohli-has-to-say-about-pakistan-bowlers-ahead-of-asia-cup-clash-4346131%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20great%20Virat%20Kohli%20feels%20one%20has%20to%20be%20at%20his%20absolute%20best%20to%20face%20a%20high%20quality%20bowling%20attack%20like%20Pakistan's.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fwhat-virat-kohli-has-to-say-about-pakistan-bowlers-ahead-of-asia-cup-clash-4346131%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fwhat-virat-kohli-has-to-say-about-pakistan-bowlers-ahead-of-asia-cup-clash-4346131%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fwhat-virat-kohli-has-to-say-about-pakistan-bowlers-ahead-of-asia-cup-clash-4346131%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Telling%20the%20Stories%20of%20Gorakhpur%20That%20Can't%20Be%20Swallowed%20up%20By%20Contemporary%20Horrors%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%