%20ongoing%20conflict.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fjanet-yellen-to-attend-g20-summit-focus-on-economy-climate-ukraine-us-treasury%2Farticleshow%2F103260192.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Findia%2Fjanet-yellen-to-attend-g20-summit-focus-on-economy-climate-ukraine-us-treasury%2Famp_articleshow%2F103260192.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Findia%2Fjanet-yellen-to-attend-g20-summit-focus-on-economy-climate-ukraine-us-treasury%2Famp_articleshow%2F103260192.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Major%20Changes%20In%20Visa%2C%20Consular%20Services%20To%20Counter%20Predatory%20Pricing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%2C%20in%20a%20move%20to%20mitigate%20predatory%20pricing%2C%20has%20tightened%20the%20rules%20for%20the%20selection%20of%20partner%20visas%20and%20consular%20service%20to%20the%20Indian%20diaspora%20and%20foreign%20visitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MEA%20is%20committed%20to%20serving%20Indians%20migrating%20and%20foreigners%20visiting%20India%20with%20an%20overarching%20vision%20to%20strengthen%20India's%20Image%20and%20reputation%2C%20to%20make%20the%20service%20more%20robust%2C%20seamless%20and%20reliable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20Indian%20Missions%20of%20the%20MEA%20are%20the%20first%20touch%20points%20for%20any%20international%20traveller%20coming%20into%20India%20-%20the%20Indian%20Citizen%20or%20Person%20of%20Indian%20Origin%20(PIO)%20and%20Foreigners%20(travelling%20to%20India)%20residing%20overseas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJyoti%20Mayal%2C%20President%2C%20of%20the%20Travel%20Agents%20Association%20of%20India%20(TAAI)%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20has%20embarked%20on%20a%20transformational%20program%20to%20reform%20and%20strengthen%20its%20tendering%20and%20evaluation%20process%20in%20a%20holistic%20manner%20to%20select%20the%20right%20outsourced%20service%20providers.%20While%20the%20focus%20lies%20on%20L1%20pricing%2C%20there%20is%20a%20strong%20emphasis%20on%20the%20four%20pillars%20of%20Quality%20Services%2C%20Sustainable%20and%20Viable%20Price%2C%20Data%20Protection%20and%20Security%2C%20and%20Ethical%20Practices%20and%20Integrity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20since%20the%20first%20impression%20of%20any%20individual%20travelling%20to%20India%2C%20the%20MEA%20must%20focus%20on%20offering%20superior%2C%20efficient%2C%20and%20cost-effective%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommenting%20on%20the%20endeavour%20she%20also%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20important%20that%20the%20first%20impression%20of%20any%20individual%20travelling%20to%20India%20or%20having%20to%20work%20with%20any%20Indian%20Mission%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world%20needs%20to%20be%20impeccable%2C%20as%20the%20government%20is%20determined%20to%20work%20towards%20delivering%20the%20promise%20of%20New%20India.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20MEA%20and%20its%20Missions%20as%20true%20representatives%20of%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20the%20world%20must%20focus%20on%20offering%20superior%2C%20efficient%2C%20and%20cost-effective%20services%20as%20perhaps%20the%20first%20step%20in%20that%20direction.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20president%20concluded%20by%20stating%20that%20India%20is%20positioning%20itself%20as%20a%20global%20leader%20in%20several%20sectors%20such%20as%20trade%2C%20cross-border%20services%2C%20citizen%20services%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20India%20marches%20towards%20a%20high%20momentum%20growth%20period%2C%20it%20will%20be%20critical%20to%20plan%20for%20factors%20that%20can%20impede%20progress%20and%20mitigate%20reputational%20and%20image%20risks%20for%20the%20Indian%20Government.%20Hence%20it%20became%20imperative%20for%20the%20government%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20quality%2C%20reliability%2C%20and%20credibility%20of%20the%20service%20providers%20it%20engages%20with%2C%20to%20ensure%20services%20are%20delivered%20effectively%2C%20efficiently%2C%20and%20in%20line%20with%20established%20standards%2C%20else%20failure%20in%20service%20levels%20can%20erode%20confidence%20and%20trust%20in%20the%20government's%20capabilities%2C%20leading%20to%20public%20dissatisfaction.%20The%20focus%20on%20quality%20also%20indicates%20that%20public%20resources%20are%20utilised%20wisely%20and%20that%20citizens%20receive%20the%20best%20possible%20value%20for%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693520760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-06%2Fjbkglilo_indian-passport-generic_650x400_07_June_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmajor-changes-in-visa-consular-services-to-counter-predatory-pricing-4346974%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%2C%20in%20a%20move%20to%20mitigate%20predatory%20pricing%2C%20has%20tightened%20the%20rules%20for%20the%20selection%20of%20partner%20visas%20and%20consular%20service%20to%20the%20Indian%20diaspora%20and%20foreign%20visitors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmajor-changes-in-visa-consular-services-to-counter-predatory-pricing-4346974%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmajor-changes-in-visa-consular-services-to-counter-predatory-pricing-4346974%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmajor-changes-in-visa-consular-services-to-counter-predatory-pricing-4346974%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Matthew%20Heineman%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98American%20Symphony%E2%80%