ffectively%20modeling%20when%20people%20should%20use%20that%20energy.%20A%205G%20connection%20enables%20this%20through%20the%20always-on%2C%20affordable%20mobile%20data%20the%20project%20uses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWavre%20isn't%20new%20to%20innovation%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20past%2010%20years%2C%20the%20city%20of%20Wavre%20has%20been%20fully%20committed%20to%20the%20digital%20transition%2C%26quot%3B%20Anne%20Masson%2C%20the%20mayor%20of%20Wavre%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BFor%20us%2C%20new%20technologies%20are%20an%20essential%20means%20of%20meeting%20the%20expectations%20of%20a%20rapidly%20changing%20world%20as%20well%20as%20the%20expectations%20of%20the%20players%20in%20the%20economy%2C%20health%2C%20tourism%2C%20and%20culture%20located%20in%20our%20territory.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20will%20also%20include%20affordable%20or%20free%205G%20internet%20access%20depending%20on%20needs%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bliving%20lab%26quot%3B%20using%20sensors%20to%20monitor%20air%20quality%20and%20better%20inform%20decisions%20about%20transport%20and%20the%20environment%20in%20the%20city.%20The%20project%20is%20part%20of%20a%20plan%20organized%20under%20a%20consortium%20between%20the%20city%20and%20the%20connected-tech%20company%20Citymesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20consortium%2C%20CONNECTOW%2C%20received%20a%20grant%20of%20%E2%82%AC3.9%20million%2C%20or%20about%20%244.3%20million%2C%20from%20the%20EU's%20Connecting%20Europe%20Facility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20project's%20participants%20have%20said%20the%20CONNECTOW%20project%20may%20transform%20Wavre%20into%20a%20fully%20smart%20city%20by%202030.%20The%20vision%20includes%205G%20communications%20as%20the%20backbone%20of%20how%20the%20urban%20area%20operates%2C%20with%20various%20elements%20of%20citizens'%20day-to-day%20lives%20feeding%20into%2C%20and%20powered%20by%2C%20the%205G%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20these%20new%20technologies%20are%20sometimes%20scary%20because%20the