0return%2C%20Russia%20would%20have%20to%20exit%20its%20military%20alliance%20with%20China%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CVery%20clear%20vision.%20I%20would%20do%20a%20deal%20that%20(Vladimir)%20Putin%20would%20say%20yes%20to%20but%20that%20actually%20advances%20American%20interests%20so%20that%20the%20United%20States%20wins.%20Here's%20what%20I%20would%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Ramaswamy%20said%20when%20asked%20how%20he%20would%20stop%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20freeze%20the%20current%20lines%20of%20control.%20I%20would%20further%20make%20a%20hard%20commitment%20that%20NATO%20will%20not%20admit%20Ukraine%20to%20NATO.%20That's%20enough%20to%20get%20Putin%20to%20do%20the%20deal.%20But%20I%20will%20require%20something%20even%20greater%20in%20return%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%2038-year-old%20multimillionaire%20biotech%20entrepreneur%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRussia%20has%20to%20exit%20its%20military%20alliances%20with%20China.%20Right%20now%2C%20we're%20pushing%20Russia%20further%20into%20China's%20hands.%20The%20Russia-China%20military%20alliance%20is%20the%20single%20greatest%20threat%20that%20the%20United%20States%20faces%20today.%20And%20so%20just%20as%20Nixon%20did%20it%20in%201972%2C%20I'll%20do%20it%20in%20reverse%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ramaswamy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPull%20Russia%20apart%20from%20China%2C%20and%20by%20the%20way%2C%20get%20Russia%20to%20also%20remove%20its%20military%20presence%20in%20the%20Western%20Hemisphere.%20Get%20out%20of%20the%20Western%20Hemisphere.%20Reopen%20economic%20relations%20with%20Russia%2C%20that's%20how%20we%20do%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian-American%20presidential%20aspirant%20said%20the%20reason%20why%20China%20is%20more%20valuable%20today%20is%20because%20the%20US%20has%20wrongfully%20cut%20off%20Russia%20from%20the%20West%20by%20bombing%20the%20Nord%20Stream%20one%20and%20two%20pipelines%20and%20also%20sanctioning%20Russ