teran%20pacer%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ishant%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F900-ishant-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3EIshant%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20played%20majority%20of%20his%20cricket%20under%20Dhoni's%20leadership%2C%20labelled%20Kohli%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20best%26quot%3B.%20While%20speaking%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jiocinema.com%2Fsports%2Fishant-on-his-evolution-through-the-years%2F3815542%5C%22%3EJioCinema's%20'Home%20of%20Heroes'%20show%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Ishant%20said%20that%20Dhoni%20groomed%20the%20fast%20bowlers%20before%20handing%20them%20over%20to%20Kohli%2C%20who%20took%20them%20to%20their%20prime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20(Kohli)%20was%20the%20best.%20When%20Virat%20was%20captain%2C%20bowling%20was%20complete.%20When%20we%20were%20playing%20under%20Mahi%20bhai%2C%20we%20were%20in%20a%20transition%20phase.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20Shami%20and%20Umesh%20were%20new%2C%20and%20only%20I%20was%20there.%20Everyone%20else%20would%20rotate.%20Bhuvi%20was%20also%20new.%20There%20is%20no%20match%20for%20Mahi%20bhai%20as%20a%20communicator.%20But%20what%20he%20did%20was%20groom%20the%20bowlers%20and%20leave%20them%20with%20Virat.%20Shami%20and%20Umesh%2C%20over%20time%2C%20became%20different%20bowlers%20and%20then%20Jasprit%20came%20in.%20So%2C%20he%20got%20a%20complete%20package.%20The%20best%20thing%20he%20did%20was%20identify%20everyone's%20traits%2C%20that%20he%20used%20to%20talk%20about%20one%20thing%20with%20one%20person%20and%20then%20Iet%20them%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ishant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2034-year-old%20added%20that%20Kohli's%20aggressive%20approach%2C%20coupled%20with%20his%20ability%20to%20identify%20roles%20of%20each%20player%2C%20made%20him%20special.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirst%20thing%2C%20he%20was%20aggressive.%20If%20you're%20bowling%20with%20the%20new%20ball%2C%20you%20can%20concede%2025%20runs%20in%20five%20overs%20as%20long%20as%20you%20take%20two%20wickets.%20The%20important%20thing%20was%20that%20he%20gave%20everyone%20defined%20roles.%20After%202021%2C%20I%20realized%20he%20wanted%20all%20of%20us%20to%20think%20out%20of%20the%20box%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20veteran%20pacer%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20record%2C%20Kohli%20(63.38)%20has%20a%20much%20higher%20win%20percentage%20than%20Dhoni%20(53.61)%20as%20captain%20of%20India.%20Only%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20a%20better%20win%20percentage%20than%20Kohli%2C%20but%20the%20former%20has%20played%20far%20less%20games%20as%20captain.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693501200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-01%2Fr8224bi8_sachin-kohli-dhoni-india-vs-australia_625x300_15_January_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fno-match-for-mahi-bhai-as-communicator-but-india-star-on-what-makes-virat-kohli-the-best-4341499%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Virat%20Kohli%20(63.38)%20has%20a%20much%20higher%20win%20percentage%20than%20MS%20Dhoni%20(53.61)%20as%20captain%20of%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A119%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fno-match-for-mahi-bhai-as-communicator-but-india-star-on-what-makes-virat-kohli-the-best-4341499%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fno-match-for-mahi-bhai-as-communicator-but-india-star-on-what-makes-virat-kohli-the-best-4341499%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fno-match-for-mahi-bhai-as-communicator-but-india-star-on-what-makes-virat-kohli-the-best-4341499%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gabon%20election%20results%20were%20a%20'smokescreen'%20for%20soldiers%20to%20oust%20unpopular%20president%2C%20analysts%20say%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%2