20Aditya%20L1%2C%20on%20September%202%2C%20at%2011%3A50%20a.m.%20from%20the%20Sriharikota%20space%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAditya%20L1%20will%20observe%20the%20solar%20corona%20from%20a%20remote%20location%20at%20the%20Sun-Earth%20Lagrange%20point%20L1%2C%20which%20is%20about%201.5%20kilometres%20from%20Earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScientists%20expect%20to%20get%20new%20information%20about%20the%20past%2C%20present%20and%20future%20of%20the%20Sun%20after%20analysing%20the%20data%20that%20will%20be%20collected%20by%20the%20solar%20mission%2C%20according%20to%20PTI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAditya%20L1%20will%20go%20up%20to%20the%20First%20Lagrangian%20point%2C%20about%201.5%20million%20km%20from%20the%20Earth%2C%20and%20transmit%20the%20data%20much%20of%20which%20will%20come%20to%20the%20scientific%20community%20for%20the%20first%20time%20from%20a%20platform%20in%20space%2C%20said%20solar%20physicist%20Prof%20Dipankar%20Banerjee%2C%20who%20is%20part%20of%20a%20team%20which%20conceptualised%20the%20mission%20more%20than%2010%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20Lagrange%20Point%201%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELagrangian%20points%20are%20where%20gravitational%20forces%2C%20acting%20between%20two%20objects%2C%20balance%20each%20other%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20the%20spacecraft%20can%20'hover'%20for%20a%20longer%20period%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20L1%20point%20is%20considered%20the%20most%20significant%20of%20the%20Lagrangian%20points%2C%20for%20solar%20observations%2C%20which%20were%20discovered%20by%20mathematician%20Joseph%20Louis%20Lagrange.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20satellite%20placed%20in%20the%20halo%20orbit%20around%20the%20L1%20point%20has%20the%20major%20advantage%20of%20continuously%20viewing%20the%20Sun%20without%20any%20occultation%2Feclipses.%20This%20will%20provide%20a%20greater%20advantage%20of%20observing%20solar%20activities%20and%20their%20effect%20on%20space%20weather%20in%20real-time%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20ISRO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20first%20space-based%20observatory%20to%20study%20the%20Sun%2C%20the%20Aditya-L1%20spacecraft%2C%20will%20be%20launched%20using%20the%20PSLV-C57%20rocket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Aditya-L1%20spacecraft%20will%20be%20equipped%20with%20seven%20payloads%20to%20study%20the%20Sun's%20corona%2C%20chromosphere%2C%20photosphere%2C%20and%20solar%20wind.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693500060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F4pt19oco_isro-aditya-l1-satellite-1200_625x300_14_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faditya-l1-mission-what-is-lagrange-point-1-the-location-from-where-isro-will-study-the-sun-4346372%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Aditya%20L1%20will%20go%20up%20to%20the%20First%20Lagrangian%20point%2C%20about%201.5%20million%20km%20from%20the%20Earth.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faditya-l1-mission-what-is-lagrange-point-1-the-location-from-where-isro-will-study-the-sun-4346372%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faditya-l1-mission-what-is-lagrange-point-1-the-location-from-where-isro-will-study-the-sun-4346372%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faditya-l1-mission-what-is-lagrange-point-1-the-location-from-where-isro-will-study-the-sun-4346372%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNo%20Sense%20At%20All%26quot%3B%3A%20PCB%20Blasted%20By%20Pak%20Greats%20For%20No%20Host%20Name%20On%20Jerseys%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20is%20facing%20strong%20criticism%20from%20fans%20and%20a%20few%20former%20players%20over%20the%20omission%20of%20country's%20name%20on%20the%20official%20Asia%20Cup%20logo%20on%20participating%20teams'%20jerseys.%20Former%20captain%20Rashid%20Latif%20was%20among%20those%20who%20lashed%20out%20at%20the%20board%20soon%20after%20the%20Pakistan%20team%20took%20the%20field%20against%20Nepal%20in%20the%20opening%20match%20of%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20in%20Multan%20on%20Wednesday.%20Though%20Asia%20Cup%20is%20jointly%20staged%20by%20Pakistan%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20the%20former%20is%20the%20host%20of%20the%20tournament.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20unacceptable%20and%20it%20is%20the%20Asian%20Cricket%20Council%20which%20must%20explain%20this%20oversight%20since%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20is%20their%20property%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20Since%20the%20hue%20and%20cry%2C%20PCB%20unofficially%20has%20tried%20to%20play%20down%20the%20situation%20by%20saying%20that%20the%20ACC%20had%20taken%20a%20decision%20after%20last%20year's%20Asia%20Cup%20that%20the%20host%20country's%20name%20would%20not%20be%20given%20with%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20logo%20in%20future%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20most%20Pakistani%20cricket%20fans%20on%20social%20media%20are%20not%20willing%20to%20accept%20this%20explanation.%20Some%20have%20even%20questioned%20that%20even%20if%20the%20ACC%20had%20taken%20such%20a%20decision%2C%20why%20did%20the%20PCB%20agree%20to%20it%20since%20Pakistan%20was%20hosting%20a%20multi-team%20event%20after%2015-years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMakes%20no%20sense%20at%20all.%20Then%20why%20has%20the%20ACC%20given%20the%20host%20country's%20name%20on%20the%20logos%20for%20their%20Asian%20Emerging%20Nations%20Cup%20or%20their%20Asian%20under-16%20event%20held%20in%20July%20in%20Malaysia%2C%E2%80%9D%20former%20Test%20batsman%20Mohsin%20Khan%20questioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohsin%20Khan%20said%20the%20ACC%20should%20clear%20the%20confusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20former%20player%20who%20didn't%20want%20to%20be%20named%20believes%20that%20Jay%20Shah%2C%20the%20President%20of%20the%20ACC%20and%20secretary%20of%20the%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%2C%20was%20the%20reason%20for%20Pakistan%20not%20being%20acknowledged%20as%20the%20host%20nation%20on%