al%20services%20GVA%20as%20of%20Q1%20this%20financial%20year%20grew%20year-on-year%20by%2012.2%25%2C%20compared%20to%20a%20figure%20of%208.5%25%20in%20the%20same%20time%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGVA%20for%20the%20agriculture%2C%20forestry%20and%20fishing%20industry%20grew%20year-on-year%20by%203.5%25%20this%20Q1%2C%20compared%20to%20last%20year%E2%80%99s%202.4%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20other%20industries%20saw%20a%20decline%20in%20their%20GVA%20growth%20compared%20to%20last%20year.%20Construction%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20clocked%20in%207.9%25%20growth%20this%20Q1%20as%20compared%20to%2016%25%20in%20the%20same%20time%20last%20year.%20The%20respective%20figures%20for%20the%20mining%20and%20quarrying%20sector%20are%205.8%25%20and%209.5%25%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20above%20figures%20were%20calculated%20using%202011-12%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIE%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20that%20a%20weakness%20in%20mining%20output%2C%20along%20with%20the%20effect%20of%20El%20Nino%20on%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20monsoon%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20temper%20GDP%20growth%20rate%20in%20the%20remaining%20quarters%20of%20this%20financial%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20press%20release%20by%20the%20NSO%20today%20(August%2031)%20said%20that%20it%20will%20release%20its%20GDP%20growth%20estimates%20for%20the%20July-September%20quarter%20this%20financial%20year%20on%20November%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693494345000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F16115416%2Frupee-g803a66102_1920.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fgdp-grew-by-7-8-pc-yoy-this-q1-nso-says%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Data%20released%20by%20the%20National%20Statistical%20Office%20also%20contains%20a%20breakdown%20of%20how%20the%20gross%20value%20added%20by%20different%20industries%20has%20changed%20year-on-year%20this%20Q1.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A