Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20previously%20had%20a%20limited%20understanding%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20migration%2C%20focussing%20mainly%20on%20the%20trend%20of%20families%20from%20Banswara%20district%20moving%20to%20Gujarat%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20primarily%20for%20construction%20work.%20Our%20prior%20knowledge%20of%20the%20working%20conditions%20for%20women%20and%20adolescent%20girls%20portrayed%20a%20grim%20picture%2C%20marked%20by%20physical%20exhaustion%2C%20persistent%20malnutrition%20(even%20during%20pregnancy)%2C%20and%20the%20constant%20specter%20of%20sexual%20harassment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20our%20conversations%20with%20women%20from%20various%20villages%20in%20Gogunda%20revealed%20a%20complex%20nature%20of%20migration%2C%20shaped%20by%20intricate%20societal%20structures.%20Some%20of%20these%20women%20we%20spoke%20with%20were%20visiting%20to%20help%20families%20for%20the%20Kharif%20crop%20season%2C%20or%20have%20returned%20to%20their%20homes%20permanently%2C%20because%20they%20dared%20to%20speak%20up%20for%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20entitlement%2C%20lack%20of%20options%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20women%20shared%20their%20diverse%20experiences%20and%20varied%20impacts%20of%20migration%20on%20their%20lives%20and%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETara%2C%20a%20mother%20of%20three%20young%20daughters%2C%20Ganga%2C%20Monika%20and%20Geeta%2C%20works%20in%20a%20hotel%20in%20Rajkot%20with%20her%20husband.%20For%20the%20last%20four%20years%2C%20she%20has%20been%20cooking%20in%20the%20hotel%E2%80%99s%20kitchen.%20She%20has%20left%20behind%20two%20of%20her%20daughters%20with%20her%20relatives%20in%20Gogunda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20only%20allow%20one%20child%20to%20stay%20with%20us%20and%20since%20Geeta%20is%20the%20youngest%2C%20she%20travels%20with%20us.%20We%20have%20enrolled%20the%20other%20two%20in%20a%20school%20there%20%5Bin%20Gogunda%5D%2C%20but%20they%20are%20not%20consistent%20because%20nobody%20keeps%