%20isn%E2%80%99t%20the%20only%20woman%20who%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20come%20back%20to%20her%20village%20after%20working%20in%20a%20big%20city%20like%20Rajkot%20or%20Ahmedabad.%20Women%20workers%20are%20torn%20between%20the%20worlds%20they%20inhabit%3B%20they%20stand%20between%20the%20societal%20expectations%20of%20leaving%20work%20for%20family%20and%20the%20different%20life%20cities%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gap%20between%20these%20two%20worlds%20is%20quite%20evident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESonu%2C%2023%2C%20a%20mother%20of%20two%2C%20came%20back%20to%20her%20husband%E2%80%99s%20village%20Dadiya%2C%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20and%20never%20went%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20first%20went%20to%20Ahmedabad%20when%20she%20was%2010%20years%20old%2C%20with%20her%20uncle%20who%20worked%20at%20the%20airport.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20not%20my%20first%20time%20living%20away%20from%20home.%20I%20went%20with%20my%20uncle%20and%20lived%20there%20for%20two%20years.%20I%20wanted%20to%20see%20the%20aeroplanes%20and%20thought%20I%20could%20study%20anytime%20but%20this%20is%20my%20only%20chance%20to%20go%20out%20and%20see%20them%20taking%20off%2C%E2%80%9D%20her%20eyes%20sparkle%20as%20she%20recalls%20those%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20after%20getting%20married%20at%20the%20age%20of%2012%2C%20she%20found%20the%20courage%20to%20speak%20up%20about%20her%20previous%20experiences.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20not%20afraid%20ma%E2%80%99am.%20During%20one%20of%20our%20jobs%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20were%20made%20to%20stay%20along%20with%20other%20men%20because%20there%20were%20not%20a%20lot%20of%20women%20working%20in%20those%20spaces%20back%20then.%20I%20raised%20my%20concern%20and%20asked%20my%20husband%2C%20who%20is%20quite%20understanding%2C%20to%20get%20work%20somewhere%20else%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20just%20had%20one%20task%20to%20do%20there%20%E2%80%93%20I%20used%20to%20clean%20the%20kitchen%20and%20in%20turn%2C%20I%20was%2