0alongside%20their%20husbands%20raises%20intriguing%20questions%20about%20the%20evolving%20migration%20patterns.%20To%20truly%20understand%20this%20shift%20and%20the%20motivation%20behind%20women%E2%80%99s%20inclusion%2C%20it%20is%20imperative%20to%20delve%20into%20the%20complicated%20ways%20in%20which%20both%20men%20and%20women%20perceive%20women%E2%80%99s%20roles%20in%20this%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20her%20decision%20to%20accompany%20her%20husband%20to%20Ahmedabad%2C%20Ganeshi%20Bai%E2%80%99s%20response%20was%20rooted%20in%20the%20belief%20that%20she%20was%20needed%20to%20assist%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEveryone%20said%20he%20is%20already%20working%2C%20and%20you%20will%20work%20in%20the%20kitchen%20only%20at%20home.%20So%2C%20why%20not%20help%20your%20husband%20with%20his%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20response%20also%20shaped%20her%20perception%20of%20her%20role%20as%20a%20wife%20and%20a%20worker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20women%20find%20themselves%20cast%20into%20the%20role%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98helper%E2%80%99.%20However%2C%20this%20seemingly%20innocuous%20term%20conceals%20a%20significant%20imbalance.%20It%20also%20reveals%20a%20subtle%20yet%20significant%20form%20of%20labour%20exploitation%20since%20it%20diminishes%20the%20magnitude%20of%20their%20work%2C%20demoting%20them%20to%20a%20position%20devoid%20of%20the%20rights%20that%20a%20recognised%20worker%20would%20command.%20This%20linguistic%20choice%20effectively%20deprives%20these%20women%20of%20the%20entitlements%20that%20should%20rightfully%20accompany%20their%20labour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Obra%2C%20a%20quite%20remote%20village%20in%20the%20block%2C%20where%20opportunities%20are%20limited%2C%20catering%20contracts%20have%20become%20increasingly%20popular%2C%20attracting%20numerous%20young%20couples%20who%20are%20hired%20by%20the%20subcontractors%20and%20contractors%20to%20cities%20like%20Rajkot%20and%20Ahmedabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHansa%2C%2022%2C%20a%20mother%20of%20one%2C%20confidently%20shares%20her%20story.%20She%20and%20her%20husband%20primarily%20earn%20from%20catering%20services%2C%20where%20they%20are%20paid%20Rs%20500%20per%20day.%20However%2C%20if%20they%20secure%20a%20monthly%20job%20at%20a%20hotel%2C%20they%20are%20paid%20Rs%2015%2C000%20combined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20said%20I%20also%20want%20to%20go%20with%20him%20because%20I%20heard%20other%20women%20from%20many%20villages%20go%20and%20help%20their%20husbands%20in%20the%20kitchen.%20I%20studied%20till%209th%20grade.%20I%20can%20keep%20an%20account%20of%20our%20salary%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20visited%20Hansa%E2%80%99s%20home%20in%20Obra%2C%20we%20were%20greeted%20by%20a%20modest%20kuccha%20house%2C%20barely%20spacious%20enough%20to%20accommodate%20her%20family%20of%20six%20adults%20along%20with%20a%20dozen%20farm%20animals.%20Such%20living%20conditions%20were%20common%20among%20families%20in%20the%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31160032%2Fimage-1265.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22701%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31160032%2Fimage-1265.png%20701w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31160032%2Fimage-1265-300x110.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-670863%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22258%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EHansa%20(left)%2C%20and%20Ganeshi%20Bai.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20came%20back%20to%20the%20village%20for%20my%20first%20delivery%2C%20which%20was%20seven%20months%20ago.%20My%20husband%20will%20go%20back%20%5Bto%20the%20city%5D%20when%20he%20gets%20some%20work.%20Then%20I%20will%20also%20go%20after%20two%20to%20three%20months%20to%20work%20%5Bin%20the%20city%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20uncertain%20nature%20of%20these%20contracts%20may%20expose%20them%20to%20an%20unreliable%20employment%20environment%2C%20Hansa%20and%20other%20women%20from%20her%20village%20do%20not%20seem%20to%20care%20about%20the%20lack%20of%20stability%20because%20of%20the%20abundant%20opportunities%20this%20migration%20offers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20an%20awareness%20about%20the%20complexities%20surrounding%20labour%20migration%2C%20the%20need%20for%20a%20consistent%20income%2C%20and%20the%20importance%20of%20labour%20rights%20are%20crucial%20for%20Hansa%20and%20her%20peers%20as%20they%20aim%20for%20a%20more%20secure%20and%20empowered%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20stories%2C%20however%2C%20raise%20an%20important%20question.%20Why%20are%20women%20now%20being%20included%20in%20these%20migration%20ventures%20when%20historically%20they%20had%20been%20kept%20out%3F%20The%20answer%20to%20this%20question%20lies%20in%20the%20concept%20of%20enlisting%20women%20as%20%E2%80%98helpers%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20strategically%20eliminates%20the%20need%20to%20hire%20two%20separate%20individuals%20for%20kitchen-related%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContractors%20keenly%20seize%20upon%20this%20ploy%3A%20by%20encouraging%20male%20workers%20to%20bring%20their%20wives%20along%2C%20they%20can%20avoid%20the%20expense%20of%20hiring%20two%20men%20because%20then%20they%20can%20pay%20two%20individuals%2C%20a%20husband%20and%20a%20wife%2C%20a%20combined%20wage%20that%20is%20often%20lower%20than%20what%20two%20male%20workers%20would%20individually%20command.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20contractors%E2%80%99%20cost-saving%20strategy%2C%20however%2C%20becomes%20unfavourable%20to%20women%20as%20it%20does%20not%20allow%20them%20to%20explore%20their%20identity%20as%20an%20independent%20worker.%20This%20approach%20also%20highlights%20how%20gender%2C%20migration%2C%20and%20economics%20intersect%2C%20showing%20the%20ongoing%20struggle%20for%20women%20to%20be%20treated%20fairly%20and%20paid%20equally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKailashi%2C%2021%2C%20shared%20her%20experience%20as%20a%20migrant%20labourer.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20not%20paid%20for%20the%20work%2C%20only%20my%20husband%20did%2C%20and%20at%20night%2C%20all%20the%20kitchen%20staff%20used%20to%20sleep%20together%20in%20the%20kitchen%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20300px)%2085vw%2C%20300px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31160302%2Fimage-1266-300x225.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31160302%2Fimage-1266-300x225.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31160302%2Fimage-1266.png%20302w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-670866%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22225%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EKailashi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20came%20back%20from%20Maharashtra%20due%20to%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20Kailashi%20found%20her%20in-laws%E2%80%99%20home%20overcrowded%2C%20with%20six%20people%20crammed%20into%20a%20single%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20demanded%20her%20husband%20to%20provide%20her%20and%20their%20son%20a%20separate%20living%20space%2C%20he%20abandoned%20her%20and%20sent%20her%20back%20to%20her%20maternal%20home.%20In%20the%20process%2C%20her%20husband%20also%20took%20her%20son%20away%2C%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20never%20wanted%20to%20get%20married%2C%20and%20now%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20I%20will%20do%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20while%20working%20on%20her%20father%E2%80%99s%20farm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKailashi%E2%80%99s%20story%20r