and%20how%2C%20perhaps%20irreversible%2C%20the%20division%20in%20Manipur%20has%20become%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%E2%80%99m%20not%20so%20sure%20yet%20whether%20the%20Naga%20MLAs%20would%20not%20attend%20the%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlthough%2C%20two%20newspapers%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20have%20suggested%20they%20wanted%20it.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20they%20do%2C%20I%20mean%2C%20it%20only%20sends%20a%20political%20signal%20of%20how%20isolated%20in%20one%20sense%20the%20Meiteis%20are%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20population%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%5B%3Cstrong%3EEditor%E2%80%99s%20Note%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20While%20the%2010%20Kuki%20MLAs%2C%20including%20two%20cabinet%20ministers%2C%20did%20not%20attend%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-assemblys-one-day-session-adjourned-after-11-minutes%5C%22%3E11-minute%20session%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%2010%20Naga%20MLAs%20did%20attend.%5D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnd%20that%20would%2C%20in%20a%20sense%2C%20bring%20home%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20India%20how%20deep%20and%20perhaps%20irreversible%20this%20divide%20is%20becoming.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20the%20division%20is%20very%20deep.%20Whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20irreversible%2C%20I%20would%20still%20wait%20to%20see%20how%20the%20developments%20take%20place%20on%20the%20various%20steps%20that%20the%20government%20needs%20to%20take%20%E2%80%93%20and%20whether%20they%20would%20take%20those%20steps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20want%20very%20much%20to%20talk%20to%20you%20about%20the%20steps%20that%20need%20to%20be%20taken%20and%20I%20want%20to%20talk%20about%20those%20steps%20in%20terms%20of%20different%20issues%20that%20occur%3A%20law%20and%20order%2C%20political%20issues%20and%20background%20issues.%20But%20before%20I%20come%20to%20that%2C%20let%20me%20ask%20you%20first%20for%20your%20assessment%20of%20the%20way%20governments%20%E2%80%93%20both%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Imphal%20%E2%80%93%20have%20so%20far%20handled%20this%20crisis.%20What%20is%20your%20assessment%20of%20chief%20minister%20Biren%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20handling%20over%20almost%20the%20last%20four%20months%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20think%20what%20we%20have%20to%20realise%20is%20that%20there%20has%20been%20a%20constitutional%20breakdown.%20The%20state%20government%20has%20been%20more%2C%20shall%20I%20say%2C%20explicit%20by%20its%20absence%20rather%20than%20its%20presence%20across%20all%20of%20Manipur%20%E2%80%93%20including%20the%20Meitei-dominated%20areas.%20And%20to%20that%20extent%2C%20what%20was%20mentioned%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%A6%20one%20of%20the%20justices%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20mentioned%20that%20there%20is%20an%20apparent%20constitutional%20breakdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FoiwYwBRakTM%3Fsi%3DX0-h6jYhas592aai%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20that%20case%2C%20should%20the%20chief%20minister%20be%20replaced%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20a%20political%20decision%20for%20the%20government%20of%20India%20to%20take.%20And%20I%20think%20with%20the%20governments%20being%20of%20the%20same%20%E2%80%93%20both%20BJP%20governments%20in%20the%20Centre%20and%20state%20%E2%80%93%20it%20is%20unlikely%20that%20if%20they%20have%20not%20taken%20a%20decision%20so%20far%2C%20that%20they%20would%20take%20such%20a%20decision%20in%20the%20future.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20the%20not-so-recent%20past%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi%20dismissed%20the%20Darbara%20Singh%20government%20in%20Punjab%20when%20she%20felt%20th