0fact%20that%20he%E2%80%99s%20been%20incompetent%20in%20restoring%20law%20and%20order%3F%20Does%20it%20make%20up%20for%20the%20fact%20that%20he%E2%80%99s%20unacceptable%20to%2016%25%20of%20his%20population%20and%20perhaps%20pretty%20close%20to%2050%25%20of%20his%20own%20MLAs%3F%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESee%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20question%20of%E2%80%A6%20one%20is%20of%20constitutional%20propriety%20and%20the%20other%20is%20the%20political%20aspects.%20And%20obviously%2C%20in%20this%20case%2C%20the%20political%20issues%20have%20taken%20priority%20over%20constitutional%20aspects%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20very%20clear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20that%20unfortunate%20in%20your%20eyes%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20unfortunate%2C%20yes%2C%20because%20it%20sends%20a%20wrong%20signal%20not%20just%20to%20Manipur.%20It%20sends%20a%20wrong%20signal%20to%20all%20the%20states%20in%20India%20and%20especially%20other%20states%20in%20the%20northeast%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20retaining%20Biren%20Singh%20is%20sending%20the%20wrong%20signal%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20I%20think.%20I%20have%20no%20doubt%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20come%20to%20the%20handling%20of%20the%20situation%20by%20the%20central%20government.%20In%20the%20speech%20that%20he%20made%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20when%20the%20no-confidence%20and%20debate%20happened%2C%20the%20home%20minister%20spoke%20for%20two%20hours%20and%20he%20explained%20the%20present%20crisis%20in%20terms%20of%20an%20influx%20of%20illegal%20refugees%20%E2%80%93%20Kuki%20refugees%20%E2%80%93%20from%20Myanmar%20from%202021.%20Now%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20doubt%20that%20is%20precisely%20how%20the%20Meitei%20believed%20the%20situation%20had%20arisen.%20But%20the%20Kuki%20have%20a%20very%20different%20explanation.%20Did%20the%20home%20minister%20make%20a%20mistake%20in%20only%20giving%20the%20explanation%20fr