20was.%20So%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%2C%20you%20know%2C%20find%20anything%20new.%20This%20has%20been%20the%20strategy%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20therefore%20he%E2%80%99s%20just%20following%20that%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20you%20explain%20that%20further%20Mr%20Pillai%3F%20You%20believe%20the%20strategy%20of%20the%20BJP%20is%20to%20side%20with%20the%20Meiti%20and%20push%20the%20Kuki%20aside%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20they%E2%80%99ve%20done%20in%20actual%20practice%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20they%E2%80%99ve%20done.%20So%E2%80%A6%20it%E2%80%99s%20something%20unfortunate%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20happened%20and%20the%20consequences%20are%20there%2C%20which%20we%20have%20seen.%20And%20now%20we%20have%2C%20in%20one%20sense%2C%20to%20pick%20up%20the%20pieces%20and%20see%20where%20we%20take%20them%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20are%20saying%20something%20very%20important%20and%20I%E2%80%99m%20only%20repeating%20it%20so%20the%20audience%20understands%20you%20fully.%20You%E2%80%99re%20actually%20saying%20the%20government%20of%20India%20has%20taken%20sides%20in%20the%20Meitei%20Kuki%20conflict%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20taken%20the%20side%20of%20the%20Meitei%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20no%20doubt%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThis%20is%20truly%20unfortunate%2C%20isn%E2%80%99t%20it%3F%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20unfortunate%20but%20that%E2%80%99s%20politics%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F24085228%2F1500x500-1.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F24085228%2F1500x500-1.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F24085228%2F1500x500-1-300x100.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F24085228%2F1500x500-1-1024x341.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-664686%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EManipur%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20(L)%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40NBirenSingh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIf%20you%20had%20been%20home%20secretary%20and%20you%20saw%20this%20happening%2C%20what%20would%20you%20have%20said%20to%20the%20home%20minister%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%2C%20I%20think%20first%2C%20the%20most%20important%20thing%20is%20that%20you%20have%20to%20maintain%20law%20and%20order.%20And%20if%20you%20find%20that%20the%20state%20government%20%E2%80%93%20because%20law%20and%20order%20is%20the%20state%20subject%20%E2%80%93%20if%20they%20are%20unable%20to%20maintain%20that%2C%20then%20I%20think%20you%20have%20to%20take%20what%20action%20follows%20from%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%E2%80%99re%20suggesting%20that%20if%20you%20were%20home%20secretary%20and%20the%20law%20and%20order%20was%20not%20under%20control%2C%20you%20would%20have%20said%20to%20the%20home%20minister%2C%20dispense%20with%20your%20chief%20minister%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes.%20I%20think%20if%20he%20could%20not%20control%20the%20situation%20and%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20went%20out%20of%20control%2C%20as%20it%20went%2C%20and%20you%20had%20a%20complete%20breakdown%20of%20law%20and%20order%2C%20then%20I%20think%20you%20really%20need%2C%20in%20one%20sense%2C%20to%20have%20dismissed%20the%20chief%20minister.%20Because%20that%20I%20think%20was..%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20impose%20President%E2%80%99s%20Rule%20but%20you%20could%20have%20got%20rid%20of%20him%20and%20brought%20in%20somebody%20else%20who%20you%20could%20try.%20And%20if%20he%20still%20failed%2C%20then%20the%20only%20other%20option%20is%20President%E2%80%99s%20Rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20I%E2%80%99ll%20sum%20up%20this%20bit%2C%20you%E2%80%99re%20saying%20two%20very%20important%20things.%20One%2C%20that%20the%20strategy%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20using%20in%20Manipur%2C%20which%20is%20to%20take%20sides%20with%20the%20Meitei%20against%20the%20Kuki%2C%20is%20the%20wrong%20strategy%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20unfortunate.%20And%20secondly%2C%20retaining%20Biren%20Singh%20as%20chief%20minister%20%E2%80%93%20which%20follows%20from%20that%20strategy%20%E2%80%93%20is%20another%20terrible%20mistake.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20it%20is.%20I%20think%20in%20the%20long%20term%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20mistake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20come%20to%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20handling.%20For%2079%20days%2C%20he%20refused%20to%20speak%20in%20public%20about%20Manipur%20%E2%80%93%20not%20a%20single%20syllable.%20Thereafter%2C%20if%20you%20count%20up%20the%20occasions%20when%20he%E2%80%99s%20spoken%20about%20Manipur%2C%20it%20comes%20to%20a%20total%20of%20under%2010%20minutes.%20Which%20means%20in%20nearly%20four%20months%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20of%20India%20has%20spent%20less%20than%2010%20minutes%20speaking%20about%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20crises%20India%20faces.%20As%20a%20former%20home%20secretary%2C%20what%20do%20you%20make%20of%20that%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20think%20the%20prime%20minister%20has%20left%20it%20to%20the%20home%20minister%20to%20take%20a%20call.%20I%20think%20this%20is%20one%E2%80%A6%20it%E2%80%99s%2C%20again%2C%20a%20decision%20that%20he%20has%20taken%2C%20He%20thinks%20the%20home%20minister%20is%20handling%20it%2C%20and%20he%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20interfere%20with%20what%20the%20home%20minister%20is%20doing.%20Therefore%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20kept%20his%20%E2%80%93%20shall%20I%20say%20%E2%80%93%20minimal%20approach%20rather%20than%20intervene%20directly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGiven%20the%20seriousness%20of%20the%20crisis%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20carried%20on%20for%20months%2C%20was%20the%20prime%20minister%20right%20to%20leave%20this%20entirely%20to%20the%20home%20minister%3F%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20a%20difficult%20call%20for%20me%20to%20make%20is%20that.%3Cspan%3E%20I%3C%2Fspan%3Et%E2%80%99s%20the%20prime%20minister%20of%20India%2C%20he%20takes%20the%20call.%20He%E2%80%99s%20politically%20very%20astute.%20So%20he%E2%80%99s%20taken%20the%20call%2C%20I%20think%20very%20deliberately%20and%20in%20a%20measured%20way.%20So%20we%E2%80%99ll%20have%20to%20see%20how%20things%20pan%20out%20in%20the%20months%20to%20come%2C%20to%20see%20whether%20that%20call%20was%20right%20or%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEarlier%2C%20when%20we%20were%20talking%20about%20the%20home%20minister%2C%20you%20said%20he%20has%20consciously%20put%20BJP%20politics%20ahead%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20constitutional%20requirements.%20That%2C%20it%20seems%2C%20is%20also%20true%20of%20Mr%20Modi%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20see%20how%20things%20go%E2%80%A6%20the%20matter%20is%20already%20before%20The%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%A6%20the%20issues%20which%20are%20coming%20%5Bup%5D%2C%20I%20think%2C%20we%E2%80%99ll%20see%20how%20it%20pans%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPractically%20everyone%20I%E2%80%99ve%20spoken%20to%20in%20Manipur%20%E2%80%93%20and%20in%20the%20last%20four%20months%2C%20I%20think%20I%E2%80%99ve%20done%20about%2030-31%20interviews%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20these%20guests%20were%20Meiti%2C%20Kuki%2C%20Meitei%20Pangal%20or%20Naga%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20all%20said%20that%20they%20feel%20let%20down%20by%20the%20prime%20minister.%20Many%20have%20said%20they%20think%20the%20prime%20minister%20has%20turned%20their%20back%20on%20them.%20One%20of%20them%20even%20said%20to%20me%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20can%E2%80%99t%20even%20see%20the%20prime%20minister.%E2%80%9D%20Then%2C%20are%20people%20in%20Manipur%20justified%20in%20feeling%20and%20thinking%20like%20this%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESee%20I%20think%20you%20are%E2%80%A6%20In%20a%20state%2C%20you%20are%20depending%20on%20the%20prime%20minister%20to%20solve%20all%20your%20local%20problems.%20They%20have%20to%20be%20solved%20at%20the%20local%20level.%20And%20I%20think%20you%20cannot%20expect%20the%20prime%20minister%20to%20solve%20the%20problem%2C%20especially%20as%20complex%20and%20complicated%20as%20Manipur%2C%20just%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%20intervening.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20matter%20which%20you%20have%20to%20solve%20yourself%2C%20and%20I%20think%20if%20you%20are%20not%20able%20to%20solve%20it%2C%20there%20are%20other%20constitutional%20remedies%20%E2%80%93%20which%20of%20course%2C%20have%20not%20been%20taken%20%E2%80%93%20but%20you%20have%20to%20solve%20the%20problem%20by%20discussion%20and%20dialogue%20among%20the%20groups%20in%20Manipur%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20last%20question%20about%20the%20prime%20minister.%20Many%20people%20say%2C%20many%20people%20in%20Manipur%2C%20that%20he%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20the%20most%20popular%20person%20in%20the%20country%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20by%20far%20the%20most%20powerful.%20Were%20he%20to%20take%20an%20initiative%2C%20were%20he%20to%20fly%20in%20for%20a%20day%2C%20were%20he%20to%20invite%20civil%20society%20organisations%20to%20meet%20him%2C%20he%20would%20give%20a%20message%20that%20he%20personally%20cares%2C%20and%20that%20would%20encourage%20people%20to%20talk%2C%20perhaps%20to%20reconcile.%20That%20initiative%20needed%20to%20be%20taken%20by%20him.%20How%20do%20you%20respond%20to%20that%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20think%20any%20prime%20minister%2C%20in%20a%20situation%20of%20this%20nature%2C%20needs%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20the%20people%20because%20they%20are%20all%20his%20%5Bpeople%5D%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20the%20prime%20minister%20of%20all%20of%20India.%20And%20therefore%2C%20he%20needs%20to%20reach%20out%20at%20the%20earliest%20when%20the%20situation%20%5Bdemands%5D%E2%80%A6%20unless%20there%20is%2C%20you%20know%2C%20the%20intelligence%20briefings%20and%20the%20other%20reports%2C%20which%20we%20are%20getting%20are%20totally%20different%2C%20in%20which%20case%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20another%20issue.%20But%20if%20the%20reports%20are%20what%20has%20come%20out%20in%20the%20newspapers%2C%20and%20has%20come%20out%20through%20the%20discussions%20that%20you%E2%80%99ve%20brought%20out%20in%20some%20of%20your%20interviews%20as%20well%20as%20the%20reports%20of%20people%20who%20have%20gone%20there%20of%20different%20parties%E2%80%A6%20it%20shows%20a%20real%20issue%2C%20possibly%20unheard%20of%20in%20post-independence%20India.%20And%20I%20think%20the%20prime%20minister%20would%20have%20been%20well%20advised%20to%20have%20intervened%20personally%20and%20then%20see%20where%20it%20goes%20from%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20you%E2%80%99re%20saying%20the%20prime%20minister%20needed%20to%20reach%20out%20in%20the%20early%20stages%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20at%20least%20I%20think%2C%20after%20the%20after%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%E2%80%99s%20visit%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3Ewhich%20was%20good%2C%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%20spending%20three%20days%20in%20Manipur%20is%20unheard%20of%20in%20any%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20the%20country%20in%20Independent%20India%20%E2%80%93%20when%20that%20didn%E2%80%99t%20work%2C%20I%20think%20the%20prime%20minister%20should%20have%20stepped%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBy%20calling%20people%20to%20him%20or%20by%20visiting%20Manipur%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20could%20have%20visited%20Manipur%2C%20he%20could%20have%20called%20people%20across%20%E2%80%93%20anyway.%20Just%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20prime%20minister%20is%20concerned%20about%20the%20situation%20would%20have%20made%20a%20tremendous%20difference.%20Because%20people%20of%20the%20Northeast%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20Meiteis%2C%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20Kukis%2C%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20Zomis%20and%20so%20on%20%E2%80%93%20all%20of%20them%20are%E2%80%A6%20the%20human%20touch%20is%20very%2C%20very%20critical%20for%20them%20%E2%80%93%20that%20somebody%20cares.%20And%20it%20would%20make%20a%20tremendous%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBy%20failing%20to%20reach%20out%2C%20by%20failing%20to%20give%20that%20human%20touch%20%E2%80%93%20to%20use%20your%20words%20that%20somebody%20cares%20%E2%80%93%20and%20let%E2%80%99s%20be%20honest%20Mr%20Modi%20is%20very%20good%20at%20doing%20it%20when%20he%20wants%20to%2C%20has%20he%2C%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Manipur%2C%20been%20irresponsible%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20would%20say%2C%20you%20see%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20call%20that%20he%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20wrong%20call%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20call%20that%E2%80%99s%20for%20him%20to%20take%2C%20because%20he%20said%20he%20would%20have%20left%20it%20to%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%20to%20take%20the%20decision.%20He%20may%20have%20felt%20that%20his%20interfering%20would%20undermine%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%E2%80%99s%20position%E2%80%A6%20I%20mean%20any%20number%20of%20reasons%20there%20could%20be.%20And%20he%20sort%20of%20felt%20that%20his%20interference%2C%20at%20the%20early%20stages%2C%20may%20have%20been%20wrong.%20I%20personally%20feel%20that%20his%20intervention%20would%20have%20had%20a%20very%20salutary%20effect%20on%20the%20situation.%20But%20that%20is%20my%20view%20%E2%80%93%20others%20may%20feel%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbsolutely.%20So%20in%20your%20personal%20opinion%2C%20he%20took%20the%20wrong%20call%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20personal%20opinion%2C%20he%20should%20have%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20people%20in%20Manipur%2C%20even%20perhaps%20visited%20Manipur.%20Or%20at%20least%2C%20he%20should%20have%20called%20everybody%20over.%20The%20least%20he%20could%20have%20done%20was%20to%20call%20everybody%20over%20to%20Delhi%20for%20talks%20in%20the%20first%20week%20or%2010%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20now%20%E2%80%93%20with%20this%20in%20the%20background%20%E2%80%93%20come%20to%20steps%20that%20are%20necessary%20to%20tackle%20the%20problem.%20And%20let%E2%80%99s%20start%20with%20the%20law%20and%20order%20issue%20because%20I%20imagine%20that%E2%80%99s%20the%20most%20immediate%20concern.%20If%20the%20home%20minister%20were%20to%20pick%20up%20the%20phone%20and%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CGopal%20Pillai%2C%20no%20one%20knows%20the%20Northeast%20better%20than%20you%2C%20no%20one%20understands%20Manipur%20better%20than%20you%2C%20what%20is%20your%20advice%20to%20me%20with%20regard%20to%20tackling%20law%20and%20order%3F%E2%80%9D%20What%20would%20you%20say%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20first%2C%20I%20think%20you%20have%20to..%20what%20shall%20I%20say%E2%80%A6%20reduce%20the%20number%20of%20arms%20with%20the%20civilian%20population.%20I%20think%20the%20number%20one%20priority%20in%20terms%20of%20law%20and%20order%20%E2%80%93%20I%E2%80%99ll%20come%20to%20the%20relief%20and%20rehabilitation%20separately%20%E2%80%93%20is%20the%20recovery%20of%20the%204%2C000-odd%20weapons%20that%20were%20looted%20from%20the%20police%20armouries.%20You%20can%E2%80%99t%20have%203%2C000-4%2C000%20arms%20floating%20around%20in%20the%20civilian%20population%20and%20expect%20the%20situation%20to%20calm%20down.%20So%2C%20that%20is%20the%20number%20one%20priority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20imagine%20that%20the%20police%20and%20the%20security%20advisors%20are%20doing%20their%20best%20to%20try%20and%20recover%20the%20weapons.%20What%20is%20it%20that%20they%20should%20be%20doing%2C%20that%20clearly%20they%20haven%E2%80%99t%20done%2C%20that%20would%20recover%20weapons%20quickly%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESee%20two%20things%2C%20as%20I%20put%20it.%20One%2C%20I%20think%20every%20single%20officer%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20armouries%2C%20from%20where%20weapons%20were%20looted%2C%20should%20have%20been%20first%20dismissed%20from%20service.%20Pure%20dereliction%20of%20duty.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20time%20it%E2%80%99s%20happened%20in%20this%20sort%20of%20case.%20Second%2C%20to%20a%20large%20extent%2C%20people%20know%20with%20whom%20the%20arms.%20You%20should%20by%20now%20have%20been%20raiding%20houses%20across%20Manipur%20to%20recover%20these%20arms%2C%20which%20has%20not%20happened.%20And%20you%20put%20drop%20boxes%2C%20I%20mean%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20most%20ridiculous%20situation%2C%20that%20after%20the%20arms%20are%20looted%2C%20you%20put%20drop%20boxes%20in%20different%20parts%20and%20expect%20the%20people%20who%20have%20looted%20the%20arms%20to%20come%20and%20drop%20the%20weapons%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20one%20aspect.%20Second%2C%20I%20think%20you%20have%20to%20start%20slowly.%20Initially%2C%20yes%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19203619%2FFyQ9vBxaIAAY1u3.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19203619%2FFyQ9vBxaIAAY1u3.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19203619%2FFyQ9vBxaIAAY1u3-300x221.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19203619%2FFyQ9vBxaIAAY1u3-1024x754.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-659022%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22884%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EGun%20drop%20box%20placed%20in%20Imphal%20Manipur.%20Authorities%20are%20asking%20people%20to%20voluntarily%20return%20snatch