20order%2C%20relief%20and%20rehabilitation.%20You%E2%80%99ve%20painted%20a%20picture%20which%20is%20deeply%20depressing.%20The%20essential%20steps%20to%20resolve%20order%20are%20obvious%20but%20they%E2%80%99re%20not%20being%20taken.%20Who%20knows%20when%20they%20will%20be%20taken%3F%20The%20steps%20for%20relief%20and%20rehabilitation%20are%20obvious%2C%20they%20are%20not%20being%20taken%20%E2%80%93%20with%20the%20exception%20of%20housing.%20Nothing%20else%20is%20really%20happening.%20So%20when%20will%20we%20have%20a%20restoration%20of%20law%20and%20order%3F%20When%20will%20people%20be%20given%20relief%20and%20rehabilitation%3F%20It%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20look%20as%20if%20there%E2%80%99s%20an%20endpoint%20in%20sight.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYeah%2C%20I%20expect%20that%E2%80%A6%20See%2C%20it%20is%20unfortunate%20because%20again%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20failure%20of%20the%20government%20that%20I%20expect%20that%E2%80%A6%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20panel%20has%20now%20given%20its%20report.%20They%20have%20pointed%20out%20the%20inadequacies%20etc.%2C%20that%20have%20now%20been%20communicated%20to%20the%20state%20government%20and%20I%20think%20next%20week%20the%20response%20of%20the%20state%20government%20and%20the%20central%20government%20will%20come%20as%20to%20what%20they%20have%20done.%20I%20expect%20that%20again%20the%20state%20government%20and%20central%20government%20will%2C%20to%20avoid%20being%20criticised%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20say%20that%20we%20are%20rushing%20some%20equipment%2C%20some%20doctors%20and%20so%20on%20and%20so%20forth%20to%20show%20that%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20just%20face-saving.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20face-saving%2C%20because%20it%20should%20have%20been%20done%20much%20before%20this%20because%E2%80%A6%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20we%20failed%20as%20a%20state%20in%20restoring%20law%20and%20order%20and%20relief%20and%20rehabilitation.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20we%20have.%20We%E2%80%99ve%20had%20riots%2C%20you%20know%2C%20100%20people%20%5Bdying%5D%20is%20not%20something%20which%20is%20people%20in%20India%2C%20the%20size%20of%20India%2C%20we%20have%20not%20faced%20before.%20But%20in%20all%20cases%20which%20have%20happened%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20in%20UP%2C%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20in%20Bihar%2C%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20in%20Kerala%2C%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20%5Banywhere%20else%5D%20%E2%80%93%20the%20State%20has%20responded%20very%20quickly.%20In%20any%20riot%20situation%2C%20the%20state%20responds%20very%20quickly%20and%20if%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20respond%20quickly%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20real%20failure.%20That%E2%80%99s%20where%20the%20administration%20%E2%80%93%20officers%20also%20%E2%80%93%20are%20responsible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThis%20is%20where%20Manipur%20is%20a%20clear%20outlier.%20We%20haven%E2%80%99t%20responded%20quickly.%20In%20fact%2C%20we%20know%20what%20we%20should%20be%20doing%2C%20and%20we%E2%80%99re%20not%20doing%20it.%20It%E2%80%99s%20very%20hard%20to%20move%20further%2C%20but%20academically%2C%20I%20will.%20I%20imagine%2C%20side%20by%20side%20with%20tackling%20law%20and%20order%20%E2%80%93%20which%20as%20you%20pointed%20out%2C%20is%20being%20done%20ineffectively%2C%20if%20it%E2%80%99s%20being%20done%20at%20all%20%E2%80%93%20the%20government%20also%20needs%20to%20turn%20its%20attention%20to%20the%20very%20difficult%2C%20intractable%2C%20political%20issues.%20Are%20the%20talks%20that%20are%20happening%20with%20the%20COCOMI%2C%20on%20the%20one%20hand%20from%20the%20Meiti%20side%2C%20and%20with%20the%20ITLF%20from%20the%20Kuki%20side%2C%20the%20right%20way%20of%20tackling%20this%20political%20issue%3F%20Or%20should%20the%20government%20be%20reaching%20out%20through%20civil%20society%20groups%20and%2C%20perhaps%20through%20highly%20regarded%20individuals%20who%20both%20sides%20respect%20like%20for%20example%2C%20Ratan%20Thiyam%3F%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESee%2C%20the%20government%20has%20started%2C%20I%20think%20to%20an%20extent%20that%20fact%2C%20that%20the%20dialogues%20have%20started%20even%20though%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20still%20with%20one%20party%2C%20one%20party%20rather%20than%20everybody%20sitting%20across%20the%20table.%20That%20stage%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20yet%20come%20because%20of%20the%20acute%20mistrust%20between%20the%20communities.%20The%20process%20has%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20think%20the%20steps%20on%20law%20and%20order%2C%20which%20I%20mentioned%20earlier%3B%20the%20steps%20on%20relief%2C%20rehabilitation%20and%20compensation.%20The%20compensation%2C%20so%20far%2C%20has%20been%20very%20inadequate.%20People%20have%20lost%2C%20I%20mean%20some%20in%20some%20places%2C%20crores%20of%20rupees%2C%20and%20you%20are%20then%20saying%20I%E2%80%99ll%20give%20you%20Rs%203%20lakh%2C%20Rs%205%20lakh%20%E2%80%93%20which%20are%20still%20not%20been%20given.%20So%2C%20this%20whole%20issue%20of%20assessing%20what%20has%20been%20the%20damage%20done%2C%20finding%20out%20who%20the%20people%2C%20etc%2C.%20This%20is%20something%20which%20should%20have%20been%20done%2C%20still%20not%20done.%20But%20let%20us%20assume%20that%20those%20are%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20all%20steps%2C%20as%20part%20of%20what%20I%20call%20as%20the%20background%20to%20the%20political%20process%2C%20which%20is%20in%20one%20sense%2C%20at%20the%20moment%20they%E2%80%99re%20talking%20of%20separate%20administration.%20I%20still%20put%20it%20as%20%E2%80%93%20if%20you%20are%20looking%20at%20the%20territory%20integrity%20of%20Manipur%20being%20preserved%2C%20you%20are%20looking%20at%20as%20greater%20autonomy%2C%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20Sixth%20Schedule%20status%2C%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20something%20more.%20These%20are%20still%2C%20I%20put%20it%20as%2C%20one-two%20years%20down%20the%20line.%20Because%20the%20Manipur%20issue%20of%20autonomy%