0But%20given%20that%20it%20is%20difficult%20for%20a%20BJP%20government%20to%20dismiss%20a%20BJP%20chief%20minister%2C%20should%20President%E2%80%99s%20Rule%20be%20imposed%3F%20Where%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20dismiss%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20but%20you%20just%20take%20over%20charge%20yourself%3F%20Or%20would%20that%20be%20no%20use%3F%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYeah%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20political%20call%20which%20they%20have%20to%20decide.%20Which%20means%20that%20you%20are%2C%20shall%20I%20say%2C%20you%20are%20unhappy%20with%20what%20the%20chief%20minister%20is%20doing.%20But%20if%20you%20are%20happy%20with%20what%20the%20chief%20minister%20is%20doing%20then%20what%20happens%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20other%20problem%20with%20President%E2%80%99s%20Rule%20is%20then%20Delhi%20would%20be%20directly%20responsible%20and%20its%20failure%20would%20be%20immediately%20obvious.%20There%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20a%20buffer%20in%20between%20any%20longer.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20true%2C%20and%20that%20is%20why%20I%20said%20all%20these%20things%20have%20to%20take%20place%20simultaneously%2C%20across%20different%20agencies%2C%20all%20ministries%20of%20the%20government%20of%20India%20because%20you%20have%20a%20huge%2C%20all-state%20crisis.%20And%20therefore%20all%20departments%2C%20at%20least%20key%20departments%20%E2%80%93%20which%20are%2C%20you%20know%2C%20health%2C%20education%2C%20water%20supply%20%E2%80%93%20Centre%20has%20to%20push%20it.%20This%20is%20something%20that%20they%20should%20have%20done%20in%20the%20first%2030%20days.%20They%20haven%E2%80%99t%20done%20it.%20They%20need%20to%20do%20it%20because%20that%20inspires%20confidence%20among%20the%20people%20that%20the%20state%20and%20the%20central%20government%20cares.%20It%20is%20very%20important%20%E2%80%93%20especially%20for%20the%20people%20of%20the%20Northeast%20%E2%80%93%20to%20feel%20that%20the%20state%20government%20and%20the%20centr