n%2C%20people%20will%20start%20to%20write.%20But%20I%20think%E2%80%A6%20and%20there%20are%20still%20many%20other%20issues%2C%20which%20I%20mentioned%20are%20the%20background%20issues%2C%20which%20are%20still%E2%80%A6%20the%20refugee%20issue%2C%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20illegal%20drug%20trade%2C%20the%20issue%20of%20forest%20rights%20and%20forest%20conservation%2C%20which%20now%2C%20again%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%E2%80%99ll%20pick%20these%20up%20with%20you%20one%20by%20one.%20But%20before%20I%20do%2C%20I%E2%80%99ll%20point%20out%20something%20that%20you%20hinted%20at%2C%20because%20it%20will%20intrigue%20the%20audience.%20Clearly%2C%20you%20believe%20there%20were%20signs%20before%20May%203%2C%20that%20the%20problem%20was%20lurking%20under%20the%20surface%2C%20that%20it%20needed%20attention%20and%20care%20and%20that%20warning%20sign%20was%20ignored.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20I%20think%20the%20signs%20were%20there.%20There%20were%20small%20clashes%2C%20there%20were%20small%20protests%2C%20there%20was%20even%2C%20you%20know%2C%20the%20issue%20of%2C%20you%20know%2C%20one%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20functions%2C%20which%20he%20was%20supposed%20to%20go%20to%20Churachandpur%2C%20where%20there%20was%20his%2C%20you%20know%2C%20the%20ground%20on%20which%20he%20was%20that%2C%20whatever%20the%20structure%2C%20the%20shamiana%20and%20all%2C%20got%20burned%20down%20etc.%20The%20warning%20signs%20were%20all%20there.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20question%20of%20how%20you%20put%20it%20together%20but%20that%E2%80%99s%20a%20separate%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F22093319%2FFzKsbspXoAcEw_0.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22706%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22ht