y%20this%20is%20a%20forest%20and%20this%20is%20not%20a%20forest%2C%20so%20there%20are%20some%20areas%20on%20which%20there%20is%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20a%20gray%20area.%20Those%20have%20not%20yet%20got%20implemented.%20Again%2C%20when%20the%20Manipur%20government%20starts%20to%20implement%20the%20new%20Forest%20Act%2C%20and%20declare%20a%20particular%20area%20as%20non-forest%20and%20so%20on%20and%20so%20forth%2C%20it%20will%20create%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbsolutely%2C%20but%20this%20is%20the%20Manipur%20government%20again%20wrongly%20pointing%20fingers%20at%20the%20Kuki%20and%20claiming%20that%20they%E2%80%99re%20encroaching%2C%20when%20in%20fact%2C%20the%20government%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20understand%20the%20style%20of%20cultivation%20the%20Kukis%20use%3F%20Is%20there%20a%20mistake%20being%20made%20in%20pointing%20a%20finger%20at%20them%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESee%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20both.%20I%20think%20you%20have%20to%20look%20at%20the%20fact%20that%20there%20is%20one%20slash-and-burn%20cultivation%20which%20is%20normal.%20Then%2C%20you%20also%20have%20some%20encroachment%20which%20is%20taking%20place.%20People%20encroach%20anywhere%2C%20I%20mean%20it%E2%80%99s%20across%20the%20world%E2%80%A6.%20When%20any%20public%20area%20is%20available%E2%80%A6.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20you%E2%80%99re%20suggesting%20that%20the%20charge%20of%20encroachment%20may%20not%20be%20wrong%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20being%20exaggerated.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20think%20it%E2%80%99s%20been%20exaggerated%20but%20I%20would%20be%20surprised%20if%20there%20was%20not%20some%20encroachment%20into%20the%20forest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20human%20nature%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHuman%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20on%20the%20three%20background%20issues%20we%E2%80%99ve%20discussed%20%E2%80%93%20refugees%3B%20involvement%20in%20drug%20trade%20and%20poppy%20cultivation%3B%20and%20encroachment%20in%20forest%20areas%20%E2%80%93%20there%20is%20an%20element%20of%20exaggeration%20when%20the%20finger%20is%20pointed%20uniquely%20and%20exclusively%20at%20the%20Kuki.%20Both%20sides%20are%20involved%20in%20the%20drug%20trade.%20The%20refugees%20are%20actually%20refugees%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20not%20coming%20to%20change%20the%20demography%20%E2%80%93%20they%20will%20go%20back%2C%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20understood.%20And%20as%20regards%20encroachment%2C%20there%20is%20some%20encroachment%20happening%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20being%20exaggerated.%20Is%20that%20correct%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20I%20think%20that%E2%80%99s%20the%20actual%20ground%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELet%E2%80%99s%2C%20then%2C%20come%20to%20the%20two%20critical%20issues%2C%20that%20are%20perhaps%20the%20last%20part%20of%20this%20interview.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFrom%20the%20Meitei%20point%20of%20view%2C%20the%20real%20concern%20is%20what%20they%20call%20the%20%E2%80%9Cland%20imbalance%E2%80%9D.%20And%20they%20think%20it%20should%20be%20resolved%20in%20terms%20of%20giving%20them%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20(ST)%20status.%20Do%20you%20believe%20%E2%80%93%20given%20your%20understanding%20of%20Manipur%20and%20its%20complexities%20%E2%80%93%20that%20ST%20status%20is%20the%20right%20way%20of%20addressing%20the%20%E2%80%9Cland%20imbalance%E2%80%9D%3F%20Or%20are%20there%20other%20ways%20that%20could%20be%20equally%20efficacious%20but%20less%20controversial%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20I%20think%20so.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%2C%20even%20among%20the%20Meiteis%E2%80%A6%20there%20was%20earlier%2C%20I%20think%20it%20was%20almost%2070%25%20of%20the%20Meiteis%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20ST%20status.%20Now%20they%20say%20it%E2%80%99s%20come%20to%2050-50%20after%20these%20clashes%20and%20so%20on.%20Land%20is%20an%20issue%2C%20no%20doubt%20about%20it.%20And%20the%20Meiteis%20have%20a%20genuine%20grievance%2C%20if%20I%20may%20put%20it%20that