20Raja%20accepted%20Islam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKirat%20Singh%20was%20given%20the%20name%20of%20Sa%E2%80%99adat%20Yar%20Khan%20by%20Aurangzeb%20in%201687%20%E2%80%A6.%20The%20chief%20temple%20of%20Kishtwar%20in%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20town%20was%20converted%20into%20a%20mosque%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kashmiri%20author%20and%20first%20registrar%20of%20Delhi%20University%2C%20G.M.D.%20Sofi%2C%20writes%20in%20%3Cem%3EKashmir%3A%20Being%20a%20History%20of%20Kashmir%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20an%20authoritative%20and%20in-depth%20history%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Rashid%20Shah%2C%20a%20local%2C%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20family%20also%20offered%20their%20daughter%20in%20marriage%20to%20Baghdadi%2C%20%E2%80%9CTwo%20sons%20were%20born%20out%20of%20Baghdadi%E2%80%99s%20second%20wedlock%2C%20and%20Asrar%20Shah%20saheb%20was%20one%20of%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocal%20residents%20delight%20in%20narrating%20Asrar%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98miracles%E2%80%99%20which%20are%20believed%20to%20have%20attracted%20people%20of%20all%20faiths%20to%20the%20Sufi%20fold%20of%20Islam.%20At%20a%20young%20age%2C%20Asrar%2C%20who%20is%20the%20direct%20descendant%20of%20Abdul%20Qadir%20Gilani%2C%20a%20widely%20respected%20Hanbali%20scholar%20from%20Iran%20and%20the%20founder%20of%20Qadiriyya%20sect%20of%20Sufi%20Islam%2C%20commanded%20the%20respect%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Kishtwar%20with%20his%20humility%20and%20miracles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20popular%20story%20has%20it%20that%20Shah%20Asrar%20brought%20to%20life%20the%20only%20dead%20son%20of%20his%20friend%20and%20a%20Hindu%20resident%20of%20Kishtwar%20merely%20by%20nudging%20him%20with%20his%20walking%20cane%20while%20chanting%20some%20Quranic%20verses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20granted%20eyesight%20to%20the%20blind%2C%20made%20walls%20move%2C%20and%20cured%20people%20afflicted%20by%20deadly%20diseases%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Haji%20Mushtaq%20Ahmad%20Shah%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20the%