esh%20Kumar%20Gupta%2C%20a%20cloth%20trader%2C%20believes%20that%20his%20Hindu%20faith%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20forbid%20him%20from%20visiting%20the%20shrine%20of%20the%20Sufi%20saint%20Shah%20Asrar%20in%20Kishtwar%20town.%20Photo%3A%20Jehangir%20Ali.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHindus%20of%20Kishtwar%20don%E2%80%99t%20confine%20themselves%20to%20temples%20only.%20It%20is%20a%20town%20of%20Sufi%20saints.%20I%20am%20a%20pujari%20at%20a%20temple%20but%20I%20also%20pay%20obeisance%20at%20Asrar%20saheb%E2%80%99s%20shrine%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Rakesh%20Kumar%20Gupta%2C%20a%20trader%20whose%20shop%20was%20allegedly%20looted%20and%20set%20on%20fire%20in%20the%202013%20communal%20riots%20in%20Kishtwar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShan%2C%20the%20local%20BJP%20leader%20who%20is%20also%20the%20chairman%20of%20Kishtwar%E2%80%99s%20Block%20Development%20Council%2C%20said%20that%20the%20shrine%20is%20a%20symbol%20of%20communal%20harmony%20in%20the%20town%20where%20Hindus%20live%20in%20majority.%20Kishtwar%20has%20witnessed%20some%20of%20the%20deadliest%20riots%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20many%20of%20them%20timed%20to%20set%20the%20tone%20for%20polarisation%20ahead%20of%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20because%20of%20the%20saint%E2%80%99s%20blessing%20that%20Muslims%20and%20Hindus%20of%20Kishtwar%20continue%20to%20live%20in%20harmony.%20There%20have%20been%20many%20ugly%20communal%20incidents%20but%20the%20two%20communities%20have%20sorted%20them%20out%20amicably%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGupta%2C%2055%2C%20a%20BJP%20supporter%2C%20believes%20that%20his%20Hindu%20faith%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20forbid%20him%20from%20visiting%20Shah%20Asrar%E2%80%99s%20shrine%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20stop%20my%20Muslim%20workers%20when%20they%20want%20to%20offer%20prayers.%20All%20religions%20teach%20us%20tolerance%20and%20respect%20for%20others.%20Politics%20has%20divided%20us%20but%20Asrar%20saheb%20continues%20to%20unite%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%2