3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EA%20team%20of%20the%20Karwan-e-Mohabbat%20(Caravan%20of%20Love)%20spent%20four%20days%20in%20violence-torn%20Manipur%20from%20July%2025%20to%20July%2028.%20This%20is%20an%20excerpt%20from%20their%20ground%20report.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Karwan-e-Mohabbat%20is%20a%20citizen%20initiative%20which%20from%202017%20has%20strived%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20victims%20of%20hate%20violence%20in%20far%20corners%20of%20the%20country%2C%20to%20offer%20solace%20and%20solidarity%20to%20the%20survivors.%20We%20spent%20in%20Manipur%20many%20hours%20listening%20to%20survivors%20in%20seven%20relief%20camps%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20what%20is%20now%20perceived%20popularly%20to%20be%20a%20%E2%80%9Cborder%E2%80%9D%20between%20the%20Imphal%20valley%2C%20home%20mostly%20to%20the%20Meitei%2C%20and%20the%20hills%2C%20inhabited%20mainly%20by%20the%20Kuki%20and%20Naga%20tribal%20peoples.%20We%20met%20scores%20of%20community%20leaders%20from%20both%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20found%2C%20in%20these%20four%20harrowing%20days%2C%20a%20Manipur%20that%20is%20beleaguered%20and%20broken.%20Nothing%20indeed%20had%20prepared%20us%20for%20what%20we%20bore%20witness%20to.%20We%20found%20a%20Manipur%20almost%20fully%20transformed%20into%20a%20war%20zone%2C%20bursting%20with%20sophisticated%20rifles%2C%20mortars%2C%20bombs%2C%20and%20massive%20daily%20mobilisation%20of%20ordinary%20civilians.%20(Even%20we%20were%20caught%20once%20within%20a%20few%20hundred%20metres%20of%20raging%20cross-fire%20and%20narrowly%20escaped).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20travels%20within%20Manipur%2C%20our%20visits%20to%20the%20relief%20camps%20and%20our%20meetings%20with%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20political%20leaders%20was%20made%20possible%20because%20of%20the%20generous%20support%20of%20two%20finest%20community%20leaders%2C%20human%20rights%20defender%20Babloo%20Loitongbam%20and%20pastor%20Reverend%20Jangkholam%20Haokip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EWatch%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fprime-minister-modi-has-failed-in-manipur-world-meitei-council-chair-heigrujam-nabashyam%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%20Has%20Failed%20in%20Manipur%3A%20World%20Meitei%20Council%20Chair%20Heigrujam%20Nabashyam%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Karwan%20team%20to%20Manipur%20included%20veteran%20journalist%20John%20Dayal%2C%20community%20physicians%20Dr%20Meena%20Isaac%20and%20Dr%20Randall%20Sequeira%2C%20community%20psychiatrist%20Dr%20Rajesh%20Isaac%2C%20Surender%20Pokhal%20from%20the%20Evangelical%20Fellowship%20of%20India%20(EFI)%2C%20Jatin%20Sharma%2C%20Director%20CES%2C%20Karwan%20Media%20Fellow%20Imaad%20ul%20Hassan%2C%20Karwan%20community%20leader%20from%20Assam%20Mirza%20Lutfar%20and%20Akanksha%20Rao%2C%20a%20Research%20Fellow%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20Equity%20Studies%20(CES)%3B%20and%20peace%20worker%20and%20author%20Harsh%20Mander.%20Each%20of%20them%20have%20contributed%20to%20this%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEntire%20villages%20of%20both%20warring%20communities%20have%20been%20razed%20to%20ashes.%20Our%20foremost%20observation%20is%20that%20the%20state%20is%20led%20by%20a%20government%20that%20has%20done%20nothing%20to%20restore%20peace%2C%20and%20ensure%20justice%20against%20people%20who%20kill%2C%20rape%20and%20destroy%20homes%20with%20unfettered%20impunity%20even%20three%20months%20later.%20The%20state%20is%20absent%20in%20its%20foremost%20constitutional%20duty%20to%20protect%20civilians%3B%20it%20is%20absent%20from%20relief%20camps.%20Instead%20the%20state%20government%20is%20often%20perceived%20to%20be%20taking%20sides%20in%20what%20is%20quickly%20escalating%20into%20a%20full-blown%20civil%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20grief%2C%20the%20rage%20and%20above%20all%20the%20hate%20on%20both%20sides%20are%20boundless.%20The%20grief%20in%20both%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20camps%20almost%20mirrored%20each%20other.%20Where%20Kukis%20were%20in%20minority%20settlements%20in%20the%20Imphal%20valley%2C%20they%20were%20surrounded%20by%20crowds%20with%20torches%20that%20set%20their%20homes%20on%20fire.%20The%20same%20happened%20to%20Meitei%20people%20who%20had%20lived%20for%20generations%20in%20the%20hill%20villages%20of%20the%20Kuki%20tribal%20people.%20The%20unbearable%20grief%20and%20rage%20of%20both%20were%20that%20neighbours%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cother%E2%80%9D%20community%2C%20with%20who%20they%20had%20lived%20for%20generations%20with%20peace%20and%20goodwill%2C%20turned%20overnight%20into%20murderous%20and%20pitiless%20enemies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31153627%2F956a11b7-b181-44e9-a115-691660a63f28_2064x1112.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31153627%2F956a11b7-b181-44e9-a115-691660a63f28_2064x1112.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31153627%2F956a11b7-b181-44e9-a115-691660a63f28_2064x1112-300x162.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31153627%2F956a11b7-b181-44e9-a115-691660a63f28_2064x1112-1024x552.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-670856%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22647%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EHoused%20demolished%20during%20the%20ethnic%20violence.%20Photo%3A%20Imaad%20ul%20Hasan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20each%20recalled%20their%20fearful%20escapes%2C%20often%20trudging%20kilometres%20with%20children%2C%20sick%20and%20old%20people%20in%20their%20backs%20in%20the%20cover%20of%20the%20night.%20They%20spoke%20of%20pregnant%20women%20who%20gave%20birth%20as%20they%20escaped%2C%20of%20hungry%2C%20frightened%20babies%20whose%20cries%20they%20had%20to%20stifle.%20They%20spoke%20of%20people%20killed%2C%20of%20people%20who%20could%20not%20survive%20the%20arduous%20journeys.%20They%20mourned%20with%20us%20daughters%20abducted%20and%20sexually%20assaulted%2C%20and%20sons%20who%20never%20returned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20was%20their%20narratives%20of%20fury%2C%20of%20congealed%20and%20settled%20hate%20on%20both%20sides%20that%20worried%20us%20the%20most.%20We%20were%20struck%20first%20by%20how%20as%20people%20grieved%20inconsolably%20about%20the%20loss%20of%20their%20homes%20and%20loved%20ones%2C%20they%20completely%20erased%20from%20their%20memories%20the%20acknowledgment%20that%20people%20of%20what%20was%20now%20the%20%E2%80%9Cother%E2%80%9D%20community%20had%20often%20suffered%20almost%20identical%20tragedies%2C%20even%20though%20the%20magnitude%20of%20loss%20and%20suffering%20endured%20by%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20people%20was%20greater.%20On%20both%20sides%2C%20people%20had%20on%20the%20one%20hand%20been%20felled%20by%20the%20violence%2C%20and%20at%20the%20same%20time%20they%20had%20also%20perpetrated%20these%20same%20atrocities.%20They%20refused%20to%20carry%20not%20just%20the%20burdens%20of%20grief%20for%20what%20was%20done%20to%20them%20but%20also%20of%20culpability%20and%20guilt%20for%20what%20they%20had%20done%20to%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20more%20gravely%2C%20we%20found%20that%20the%20same%20narratives%20of%20the%20evil%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cother%E2%80%9D%20community%20were%20articulated%20whether%20we%20spoke%20to%20community%20leaders%2C%20students%2C%20women%20or%20residents%20of%20relief%20camps.%20The%20narratives%20of%20the%20Meitei%20people%20were%20that%20the%20Kuki%20people%20were%20foreigners%20who%20had%20illegally%20immigrated%20from%20Myanmar%20and%20would%20one%20day%20outnumber%20the%20indigenous%20Meitei%20people%20to%20whom%20Manipur%20belonged%20rightfully.%20They%20had%20benefitted%20from%20reservations%20for%20tribal%20people%20to%20capture%20jobs%20and%20seats%20in%20educational%20institutions%2C%20while%20the%20Meitei%20are%20prohibited%20even%20from%20buying%20land%20in%20the%20hills.%20They%20accuse%20them%20of%20endangering%20Meitei%20youth%20by%20illegal%20poppy%20cultivation.%20They%20allege%20that%20the%20Kuki%20people%20are%20illegally%20clearing%20reserved%20forests%20for%20their%20farms%20and%20settlements%2C%20and%20threatening%20the%20ecology%20of%20the%20region.%20They%20claim%20that%20Kuki%20militants%20roam%20freely%2C%20and%20their%20violence%20and%20gun%20and%20drug%20trafficking%20thrive%20under%20the%20protection%20of%20the%20Assam%20Rifles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EWatch%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-karan-thapar-gopal-krishna-pillai-manipur-clashes%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98BJP%20Government%20Siding%20With%20Meitei%20Against%20Kuki%3B%20Modi%20Was%20Wrong%20Not%20To%20Reach%20Out%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kuki%20people%20have%20an%20entirely%20different%20narrative.%20They%20allege%20that%20their%20farmers%20may%20cultivate%20poppies%20for%20bare%20survival%2C%20but%20that%20the%20drug%20trade%20and%20profits%20are%20mostly%20harvested%20by%20politicians%20and%20big%20business%20in%20the%20Imphal%20valley%20and%20beyond.%20They%20claim%20to%20be%20legal%20citizens%20of%20Manipur%2C%20and%20allege%20that%20Meitei%20people%20want%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20status%20to%20grab%20their%20lands%20and%20reduce%20them%20to%20a%20minority%20in%20their%20mountain%20abodes.%20They%20also%20want%20to%20corner%20the%20seats%20in%20the%20legislatures%20and%20educational%20institutions%20that%20are%20reserved%20for%20tribal%20people.%20They%20also%20allege%20that%20a%20militia%20of%20Meitei%20youth%20is%20actively%20supported%20by%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Manipur%2C%20and%20that%20with%20open%20state%20patronage%2C%20it%20is%20these%20militants%20who%20ravaged%20their%20lands%20and%20people%20with%20rape%2C%20murder%20and%20arson.%20They%20allege%20long%20years%20of%20work%20by%20the%20RSS%20to%20convert%20Meitei%20nationalism%20into%20Hindu%20nationalism%20implacably%20hostile%20to%20the%20Kuki%20people%20also%20for%20their%20Christian%20faith.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31153825%2F29e7e921-a549-43b2-9844-c304a34d33fe_2067x1120.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31153825%2F29e7e921-a549-43b2-9844-c304a34d33fe_2067x1120.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31153825%2F29e7e921-a549-43b2-9844-c304a34d33fe_2067x1120-300x163.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31153825%2F29e7e921-a549-43b2-9844-c304a34d33fe_2067x1120-1024x555.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-670857%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22650%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EHoused%20demolished%20during%20the%20ethnic%20violence.%20Photo%3A%20Imaad%20ul%20Hasan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20they%20believe%20that%20the%20Manipur%20state%20police%20and%20paramilitary%20forces%20protect%20the%20Meitei%20militants%20and%20those%20who%20raped%20and%20murdered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20narratives%20about%20the%20same%20lived%20reality%20are%20so%20utterly%20irreconcilable%2C%20that%20as%20long%20as%20people%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20conflict%20are%20not%20willing%20to%20step%20down%20a%20few%20steps%20from%20what%20today%20passionately%20uphold%20as%20the%20truth%20of%20the%20evil%20%E2%80%9Cother%E2%80%9D%2C%20there%20is%20no%20space%20for%20even%20a%20dialogue%20to%20begin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20midst%20of%20all%20of%20this%2C%20the%20state%20government%20has%20done%20nothing%20to%20establish%20and%20support%20the%20relief%20camps%20especially%20for%20an%20estimated%20twenty%20thousand%20Kuki%20internal%20refugees%20who%20have%20fled%20after%20their%20villages%20have%20been%20burnt%20down.%20It%20is%20largely%20the%20local%20church%2C%20supported%20by%20local%20contributions%2C%20that%20are%20running%20more%20than%20a%20hundred%20Kuki%20relief%20camps.%20Children%20in%20these%20camps%20have%20been%20reduced%20to%20eating%20watery%20rice%20with%20salt.%20Signs%20of%20malnutrition%20are%20already%20unmistakable.%20No%20camps%20have%20temporary%20schools.%20The%20refusal%20of%20the%20state%20(and%20central%20governments)%20to%20establish%20camps%20with%20basic%20services%20of%20safety%2C%20sanitation%2C%20nutrition%2C%20education%20and%20health%20care%20is%20another%20disgraceful%20abdication%20by%20the%20state%20of%20its%20fundamental%20constitutional%20duties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20searched%20desperately%20for%20signs%20of%20hope%20in%20Manipur%20for%20peace%20and%20healing%20in%20the%20immediate%20future.%20We%20could%20find%20this%20only%20in%20stories%20we%20heard%20in%20the%20camps%20of%20people%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cother%E2%80%9D%20community%20who%20helped%20save%20lives.%20These%2C%20and%20the%20acknowledgment%20of%20their%20shared%20suffering%20and%20indeed%20their%20shared%20belonging%2C%20alone%20can%20create%20the%20space%20even%20for%20the%20start%20of%20any%20dialogue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20grieve%20for%20our%20people.%20We%20grieve%20for%20our%20critically%20fractured%20land.%20We%20rage%20for%20the%20malign%20governments%20that%20we%20have%20installed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31154026%2F1c13ccf9-051a-4b3c-80ea-a49bbff34074_2067x1151.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31154026%2F1c13ccf9-051a-4b3c-80ea-a49bbff34074_2067x1151.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31154026%2F1c13ccf9-051a-4b3c-80ea-a49bbff34074_2067x1151-300x167.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31154026%2F1c13ccf9-051a-4b3c-80ea-a49bbff34074_2067x1151-1024x570.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-670858%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22668%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20relief%20camp%20in%20Moirang.%20Mnaipur.%20Photo%3A%20Imaad%20ul%20Hasan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20will%20require%20extraordinary%20statesmanship%20to%20douse%20the%20fires%20that%20burn%20across%20Manipur%2C%20and%20to%20heal%20the%20fractures%20that%20tear%20it%20apart.%20The%20present%20state%20government%20%E2%80%93%20whose%20impartiality%20and%20competence%20are%20gravely%20in%20doubt%20%E2%80%93%20needs%20urgently%20to%20be%20dismissed.%20Special%20investigation%20teams%20%E2%80%93%20including%20police%20officers%20from%20outside%20the%20state%20and%20monitored%20by%20retired%20judges%20of%20the%20higher%20courts%20%E2%80%93%20need%20to%20investigate%20the%20crimes%20of%20the%20looting%20of%20armouries%2C%20murder%20and%20sexual%20violence%2C%20and%20the%20burning%20and%20looting%20of%20villages%20and%20homes.%20Civilian%20populations%20need%20to%20be%20urgently%20and%20extensively%20disarmed.%20Leaders%20of%20both%20estranged%20communities%20need%20to%20be%20brought%20together%20to%20restore%20a%20process%20of%20dialogue.%20These%20are%20just%20the%20first%20necessary%20steps%20to%20begin%20the%20long%20journey%20to%20restoring%20peace%20to%20broken%20Manipur.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-is-in-the-dark-the-ban-on-the-internet-must-be-lifted%5C%22%3EManipur%20Is%20in%20the%20Dark%2C%20the%20Ban%20on%20the%20Internet%20Must%20Be%20Lifted%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20all%20of%20this%20is%20not%20the%20subject%20of%20this%20report%20of%20the%20Karwan-e-Mohabbat.%20There%20is%20no%20evidence%20that%20the%20steps%20we%20have%20outlined%20above%20to%20change%20the%20leadership%2C%20to%20investigate%20crimes%2C%20and%20to%20disarm%20populations%2C%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20undertaken%20in%20the%20immediate%20future.%20Without%20these%2C%20it%20would%20be%20impossible%20to%20rebuild%20trust%20between%20communities%20and%20a%20sense%20of%20safety%20that%20would%20enable%20the%20internally%20displaced%20populations%20to%20return%20to%20their%20villages%20and%20restart%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20focus%20of%20the%20recommendations%20of%20this%20report%20is%20therefore%20centred%20on%20the%20immense%20humanitarian%20crisis%20that%20we%20encountered%20in%20Manipur.%20More%20than%2060%2C000%20people%20have%20been%20displaced%20from%20their%20villages%20and%20homes.%20Most%20of%20these%20have%20been%20looted%20and%20razed%20to%20the%20ground.%20A%20majority%20of%20these%20displaced%20persons%20are%20living%20in%20relief%20camps.%20The%20state%20is%20almost%20completely%20absent%20from%20these%20camps%2C%20even%20more%20starkly%20from%20the%20camps%20in%20the%20hills.%20Since%20there%20is%20little%20chance%20today%20that%20relief%20camps%20will%20be%20wound%20up%20and%20normalcy%20restored%20in%20the%20coming%20months%2C%20the%20focus%20of%20our%20report%20is%20on%20the%20humanitarian%20crisis%20of%20the%20internally%20displaced%20persons%2C%20and%20what%20we%20are%20convinced%20must%20be%20done%20immediately%20to%20alleviate%20and%20prevent%20further%20human%20suffering%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERead%20the%20full%20report%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkarwanemohabbat.substack.com%2Fp%2Fthe-humanitarian-crisis-in-manipur%3Futm_campaign%3Dpost%26utm_medium%3Dweb%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693479561000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31154258%2F07661751-2f5a-4ec2-b554-88041bb8e9b6_3334x1870.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fvoices-from-the-ground-the-humanitarian-crisis-in-manipur%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20team%20of%20the%20Karwan-e-Mohabbat%20(Caravan%20of%20Love)%20spent%20four%20days%20in%20violence-torn%20Manipur%20from%20July%2025%20to%20July%2028.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fvoices-from-the-ground-the-humanitarian-crisis-in-manipur%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Revealed%3A%20Why%20Europe's%20wild%20boars%20are%20radioactive%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693476780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F08%2F768x432%2Fskynews-wild-boar-germany_6268987.jpg%3F20230831111935%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fwhy-europes-wild-boars-are-radioactive-12951388%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20decades%2C%20high%20levels%20of%20radioactivity%20have%20been%20found%20in%20wild%20boars%20across%20central%20Europe%20-%20and%20a%20new%20study%20explains%20why.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A137%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fwhy-europes-wild-boars-are-radioactive-12951388%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fwhy-europes-wild-boars-are-radioactive-12951388%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fwhy-europes-wild-boars-are-radioactive-12951388%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SC%20Pulls%20Up%20Gujarat%20HC%20for%20Granting%20Bail%20to%20Murder%20Accused%20Based%20on%20'Personal%20Settlement'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25222448%2FSupreme-Court-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20pulled%20up%20Gujarat%20high%20court%20for%20granting%20bail%20to%20an%20accused%20in%20a%20murder%20case%20based%20on%20a%20%E2%80%98personal%20settlement%E2%80%99%20between%20the%20accused%20and%20the%20son%20of%20the%20deceased.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20quashing%20the%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20order%20and%20ordering%20the%20accused%20to%20surrender%20immediately%20before%20the%20trial%20court%2C%20it%20also%20admonished%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20for%20not%20challenging%20the%20bail%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CStrangely%20enough%20one%20of%20the%20considerations%20that%20has%20weighed%20with%20the%20learned%20Single%20Judge%20includes%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20respondent%20No.%202%20%5Bthe%20accused%5D%20has%20filed%20a%20settlement%20arrived%20at%20with%20the%20original%20complainant%20%5Bson%20of%20the%20deceased%5D%20and%20the%20affidavit%20of%20the%20original%20complainant%20confirmed%20the%20said%20settlement%2C%20that%20too%20in%20respect%20of%20an%20offence%20under%20Section%20302%20%5Bpunishment%20for%20murder%5D%20of%20the%20IPC%20%5BIndian%20Penal%20Code%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20apex%20court%20said%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Fsupreme-court%2Fsupreme-court-surprised-by-gujarat-hc-granting-bail-to-murder-accused-based-on-settlement-with-victims-son-chastises-state-for-not-challenging-order-236632%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3ELivelaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20reached%20the%20division%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Hima%20Kohli%20and%20Justice%20Rajesh%20Bindal%20at%20the%20top%20court%20when%20one%20of%20the%20injured%20persons%20in%20the%20crime%20appealed%20against%20the%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20bail%20order.%20The%20accused%20attacked%20Parvinbahi%20(the%20deceased)%20and%20the%20appellant%20on%20September%2017%2C%202021.%20While%20the%20appellant%20sustained%20injuries%2C%20Parvinbhai%20succumbed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20also%20objected%20to%20the%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20observations%20made%20in%20the%20bail%20order%20that%20there%20are%20no%20criminal%20antecedents%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20accused%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20the%20accused%20was%20arrested%20after%20being%20released%20on%20bail%20in%20connection%20with%20another%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR).%20While%20noting%20that%20the%20accused%20had%20spent%20%E2%80%9Cmerely%E2%80%9D%20six%20months%20in%20jail%20from%20September%2023%2C%202021%20to%20February%2018%2C%202022%2C%20the%20apex%20court%20said%20there%20is%20a%20propensity%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20accused%20towards%20criminal%20behaviour%20and%20must%2C%20therefore%2C%20surrender%20promptly%20before%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20pulled%20up%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20for%20not%20approaching%20the%20court%2C%20challenging%20the%20bail%20order.%20It%20issued%20orders%20to%20authorities%20concerned%20to%20forward%20the%20latest%20order%20to%20the%20home%20secretary%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20our%20mind%2C%20this%20was%20a%20fit%20case%20where%20respondent%20No.1%20%5BState%5D%20ought%20to%20have%20approached%20this%20Court%20against%20the%20order%20of%20bail%20granted%20by%20the%20High%20Court%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20respondent%20No.2%20%5Bthe%20accused%5D%20but%20surprisingly%2C%20no%20steps%20were%20taken.%20A%20copy%20of%20this%20order%20shall%20be%20forwarded%20by%20learned%20counsel%20for%20respondent%20No.%201%20%5BState%5D%20to%20the%20Secretary%20(Home)%2C%20Government%20of%20Gujarat%20for%20his%20perusal%20and%20appropriate%20action%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693476003000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25222448%2FSupreme-Court-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-pulls-up-gujarat-hc-for-granting-bail-to-murder-accused-based-on-personal-settlement%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20top%20court%20also%20came%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20for%20not%20challenging%20the%20bail%20order.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-pulls-up-gujarat-hc-for-granting-bail-to-murder-accused-based-on-personal-settlement%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20state%20of%20Georgia%20officially%20declares%20October%20as%20'Hindu%20Heritage%20Month'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693475443000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103244675%2Cimgsize-1101552.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-state-of-georgia-officially-declares-october-as-hindu-heritage-month%2Farticleshow%2F103244485.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103244485.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20US%20state%20of%20Georgia%20has%20officially%20declared%20October%20as%20the%20%26quot%3BHindu%20Heritage%20Month%26quot%3B%20to%20acknowledge%20the%20contributions%20of%20the%20vibrant%20Hindu-American%20community%20in%20the%20state.%20In%20a%20proclamation%2C%20Governor%20Brian%20Kemp%20declared%20October%20as%20the%20'Hindu%20Heritage'%20month.%20It%20said%20that%20the%20Hindu%20heritage%20will%20be%20celebrated%20by%20focusing%20on%20its%20culture%20and%20the%20diverse%20spiritual%20traditions%20rooted%20in%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-state-of-georgia-officially-declares-october-as-hindu-heritage-month%2Farticleshow%2F103244485.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fwor