ats%C2%A0%3Cem%3EBanglar%20Mati%20Banglar%20Jol%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0as%20their%20state%20song%20and%20welcomed%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20proposal.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20if%20the%20government%20adopts%20the%20song%20with%20changed%20lyrics%2C%20we%20will%20continue%20with%20the%20original.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20most%20deserving%20to%20be%20our%20state%20song%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20the%20government%20has%20taken%20a%20number%20of%20steps%20that%20Bangla%20Pokkho%20and%20other%20Bengali%20ethnic%20rights%20groups%20like%20Jatiyo%20Bangla%20Sammelan%20had%20demanded.%20These%20included%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwbpsc.gov.in%2FDownload%3Fparam1%3DAn_20220614181059_BengaliIneliClerkship.pdf%26param2%3Dadvertisement%5C%22%3Emaking%20Bengali%20or%20Nepali%20mandatory%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20West%20Bengal%20Civil%20Service%20(WBCS)%20exams%20and%20in%20the%20recruitment%20of%20police%20constables%2C%20besides%20introducing%20a%20domicile%20quota%20in%20for%20admission%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fkolkata%2Fju-engg-gets-state-nod-for-90-domicile-quota%2Farticleshow%2F69589102.cms%5C%22%3Eengineering%20department%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0of%20Jadavpur%20University%20and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fwest-bengal%2Fcalcutta%2Fcalcutta-university-sets-domicile-term-for-tech-entry%2Fcid%2F1800919%5C%22%3EBTech%20course%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0of%20Calcutta%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20veteran%20TMC%20leader%2C%20however%2C%20claimed%20that%20the%20key%20reason%20Banerjee%20did%20not%20want%20the%20word%20Bengali%20in%20the%20song%20is%20that%20it%20could%20trigger%20fresh%20trouble%20in%20the%20Darjeeling%20hills%2C%20which%20have%20remained%20largely%20peaceful%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years%20after%20months%20of%20violence%2C%20destruction%20and%20%3Cem%3Ebandhs%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%202017%2C%20the%20wounds%20of%20which%2