n-disability-pride-and-representation-in-cinema%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emultiple%20disabilities%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20traits%20of%20Autism.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mumbai%20resident%20seems%20to%20have%20unshakeable%20resolve%20as%20she%20talks%20about%20embracing%20life%20as%20it%20is%2C%20powering%20through%20challenges%20every%20day%2C%20and%20the%20learnings%20she%20has%20had%20since%20Viha%E2%80%99s%20birth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20Viha%E2%80%99s%20early%20years%20until%202009%2C%20Sejal%E2%80%99s%20routine%20was%20constant%2C%20to%20say%20the%20least.%20Every%20morning%20the%20two%20would%20make%20their%20way%20to%20the%20Helen%20Keller%20Institute%20at%20Byculla%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20where%20Viha%20would%20be%20trained%20in%20the%20nuances%20of%20basic%20skills%2C%20speaking%2C%20interacting%20with%20others%20and%20daily%20tasks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOwing%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325345%2Fdelhi-tarini-malhotra-started-nai-subah-foundation-ngo-for-neurodivergent-community-get-jobs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eher%20disabilities%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Viha%20had%20never%20been%20admitted%20in%20a%20mainstream%20school.%20The%20Helen%20Keller%20Institute%20was%20her%20%E2%80%98home%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20was%20about%20to%20change.%20As%20the%20institute%20informed%20Sejal%20that%20day%2C%20it%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20continue%20helping%20Viha%20beyond%20the%20age%20of%20seven.%20If%20Sejal%20was%20keen%20to%20continue%20Viha%E2%80%99s%20special%20education%20with%20them%2C%20she%20would%20have%20to%20move%20her%20to%20the%20Vashi%20branch.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTravelling%20to%20Vashi%20every%20day%20with%20a%20disabled%20child%20is%20not%20conducive%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sejal%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20she%20saw%20as%20a%20hurdle%20at%20the%20time%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20the%20%3Ca