%20that%20paid%20him%20crores%20every%20year%2C%20he%20recalls.%20But%20the%20experiences%20he%20had%20had%20growing%20up%20pushed%20him%20to%20quit%20his%20job%20early%20this%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20discuss%20this%20turn%20of%20events%2C%20he%20recounts%20an%20anecdote%20%E2%80%94%20his%20grandparents%20would%20always%20start%20their%20day%20with%20a%20steaming%20cup%20of%20%3Cem%3Echai%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20two%20biscuits.%20%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20no%20one%20thinks%20about%20the%20ingredients%20present%20in%20these%20biscuits%2C%20or%20how%20much%20sugar%20or%20maida%20they%20might%20contain.%20Most%20biscuits%20in%20the%20market%20also%20have%20palm%20oil.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20the%20once-in-a-week%20chocolate%20that%E2%80%99s%20making%20you%20unhealthy%2C%20but%20actually%20are%20the%20daily%20biscuits%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cognisance%20of%20this%20undetected%20evil%20encouraged%20Revant%20to%20pursue%20a%20course%20in%20nutrition%20from%20the%20Institute%20of%20Integrative%20Nutrition%20alongside%20his%20management%20degree%20from%20the%20NYU%20Stern%20School%20of%20Business.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20solving%20business%20problems%20as%20a%20management%20consultant%2C%20%5Bbut%5D%20I%20wanted%20to%20use%20the%20same%20skills%20to%20solve%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20problems%20in%20life%20%E2%80%94%20health.%20The%20blatant%20lies%20used%20by%20food%20companies%20in%20their%20packaging%20really%20bothers%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20this%20passion%20that%20led%20him%20to%20create%20the%20infamous%20viral%20video%20in%20April%20this%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20label%20on%20that%20drink%20says%20that%20you%20get%20stronger%20bones%20and%20muscles.%20The%20reason%20I%20chose%20to%20make%20a%20video%20on%20this%20drink%20is%20because%20people%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F301227%2Fharvard-law-mba-grad-empower-underprivileged-kids-to-eat-healthy-through-games-foodshaala-foundation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efeel%20this%20is%20healthy%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20have%20no%20qualms%20about%20giving%20this%20twice%20a%20day%20to%20their%20children%20%E2%80%94%20that%E2%80%99s%2014%20times%20a%20week.%20People%20think%20aerated%20drinks%20like%20coke%20are%20unhealthy%2C%20which%20we%20may%20have%20only%20once%20a%20week.%20But%20the%20former%20has%20a%20direct%20impact%20on%20our%20health%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20Instagram%20%40foodpharmer%2C%20Revant%20educates%20about%20500%2C000%20of%20his%20followers%20on%20how%20they%20can%20make%20healthier%20choices.%20These%20include%20videos%20decoding%20labels%20of%20popular%20packaged%20noodles%2C%20drinks%2C%20biscuits%2C%20sauces%20and%20more%2C%20as%20well%20as%20helping%20people%20decide%20which%20bread%20is%20better%20for%20them%2C%20which%20drink%20they%20can%20choose%2C%20etc.%20He%20is%20also%20promoting%20small%20businesses%20that%20are%20%E2%80%9Crelatively%20healthier%E2%80%9D%20than%20the%20bigger%20brands.%20His%20goal%20is%20to%20help%20people%20choose%20better%2C%20he%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERemember%20this%20next%20time%20you%E2%80%99re%20at%20the%20supermarket%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCwChJrSNO2I%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCwChJrSNO2I%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20th